Umbono kaSiso ngomhlaba, isikhungo samanzi umbukiso omusha wegalari
Abantu babhukuda echibini lokubhukuda kusukela ngo-2022 kungumsebenzi wobuciko ka-Vicente Siso ozokhonjiswa e-Tierra del Sol Gallery kusukela ngo Jan. 13. (isithombe sihloniswa ngu-Vicente Siso)
I-Tierra del Sol iyakuthokozela ukwethula u-''Vicente Siso: Izinkumbulo Zomhlaba Namanzi'' endaweni entsha e-galllery location e-West Hollywwod. U-Siso ubengumculi ohlelweni lobuciko be-Studio kusukela ngo-2012, lokhu kuphawula umbukiso wesekela lakhe yedwa. U-Siso wazalwa ngo-1962 e-Madrid fuithi wakhulela phakathi e-Venezuela,Trinidad kanye ne-Miami, bahamba nomndeni wakhe baya e-Sourthen California esemnyakeni esekuqaleni yama-20s.
Ngokusebenza ngobuhlakani ezihlokweni ezihlukene, USiso udale uchungechunge oluhle lwezindawo, imidwebo kanye nemisebenzi yokuphila engapheli ehlanganiswe noma i-acrylic, iphasteli, ipensela noma umbala wamanzi.Esusela umsebenzi wakhe ezithombeni zomndeni, izithombe zakhe zokuzikhumbuza, kanye nokukhumbula ukwakheka kwakhe okumibalabala kukhombisa ububanzi bezintshisekelo namakhono akhe kuyo yonke imidiya. Izindawo ezishisayo nezindawo zasolwandle zikaSiso zibonisa izindawo zomhlaba zesikhathi sakhe esedlule, zisebenzisa amaphethini acebile futhi zihlanganisa nabantu ukwenza ukuxhumana okunenqondo phakathi kwesiko, inkumbulo, kanye nemvelo.U-Siso uqamba umsebenzi wakhe wezobuciko ngokuxuba iSipanishi neSingisi, okubonisa ubunzima bokuphila kwakhe okudumile nokungafani ezweni laseLos Angeles. ''UVicente Siso: izinkumbulo zomhlaba namanzi'' zivula ngoMgqibelo, Jan.13. nokwamukela kusukela ngo 6-8 ebusuku. Lo mbukiso uzoqala ukubonakala ngeSonto, Mashi 3.
ITierra del Sol Gallery iku-7414 Santa Monica Blvd. Ukuze wazi kabanzi ngayo, vakashela ku-tierradelsolgallery.org.
Lungisa okwakudala, uhlanganise okusha ukuze uxazulule inkinga
Ezingeni lesifunda sibheka i-Sydney CBD njengesibonelo sendawo ethuthukile isuka endaweni yayo yangaphambi kokuba kokuhlalwe kuyo yaba idolobha elinezitezi ezimbili,kusukela ekuphakameni okuphezulu kwama mitha angu-150 kuya emibhoshongweni ekhuphukayo yanamuhla. Ezingeni elincishisiwe okufanayo kungenzeka emadolobheni aseSydney aseduze nama-node ezokuthutha. I-Inner suburb nayo kumele iguquke ngokuguqukela ezindlini ezingabizi kakhulu ezihlala ezindaweni eziphakeme ezingaphansi kwezihlahla ezindaweni ezibalulekile.
Uhlelo lwethu lokuhlela ludinga futhi ukuzivumelanisa nezimo ukuze abahleli emukhandlwini engaphansi kwamadolobha, babonakala bengakwazi ukushintshashintsha, kungabi ibona kuphela abanquma ukuma kwekusasa kwendawo abahlala kuyo.Indlela eya phambili kungaba ukuba nenhlangano ezimele ethatha izinqumo emele idizayini yekhwalithi inqobo nje uma ngifaka iziqongo zesihlahla esingezansi futhi ngihlanganise ukuhlala komndeni. Ovilanda abakhulu, izingadi ezivamile kanye nesethulo esibukeka kahle. Lokhu kungaba yindima yomakhi wamanje we-NSW osebenza ngaphakathi kwe khodi yokuthobela eyakhiwe ngokucophelela.
Eminyakeni eyishumi eyedlule indlela yethu yokuphila iye yashintsha ngenxa yobuchwepheshe, nabaningi abasebenzela emakhaya, futhi iSydney ike yazuza inethiwekhi emangalisayo yezitimela ezihamba ngaphansi komhlaba nezinhlelo zezitimela ezilula.Ikhono lethu lokuthenga nge-inthanethi lishintshe indlela esithenga ngayo, futhi abangane nomndeni babonakale besondelene ngenxa yokuxhumana ngezincingo ezihlakaniphile. konke lokhu ukulungiswa kwesimo esisodwa kuya kwesinye kungenzeka nasendaweni yethu eyakhiwe ngokugxila ekuhleleni ekusetshenzisweni kabusha kokuzivumelanisa kunokukhetha ukulondolozwa kwamagugu.
UChris Johnson wayengumakhi wezakhiwo wase-NSW (1995-2005) kanye nomqondisi ophethe, umnyango wezokwakha wase-NSW (2005-2009). Wayengu-CEO we-Urban Taskforce Australia phakathi kuka-2011 kanye no-2019.
Umfutho wokugcina wokulingana kwabesifazane
Ngonyaka odlule, uqagulo lweorld Economic Forum lwabikikezela ukuthi kwakuzothatha izinkulungwane ezinhlanu ukufeza ukulingana kobulili kuzo zonke izizwe. Manje iWorld Bank ifuna ukusheshisa leso sikhathi.
Isikhungo sezezimali samazwe omhlaba sikulungele ukwethula isu elihlose ukuthuthukisa kakhulu amalungelo nama thuba ezomnotho amantombazane nabesifazane ngo-2030. Lolu hlelo lugxile ekuthuthukiseni ukubandakanya kanye nokuqina ngokutholakala kwezimali, ubuchwepheshe obusha, kanye nezinguquko emthethweni yomphakathi nasemthethweni.
Ucwaningo lwakamumva lubonisa ukuthi kokubili izidingo zomphakathi kanye nendlela yokucabanga ingashintsha, isibonelo, ukuthi ukubandakanywa kwamadoda kanye nabafana kungakhuthaza ukwesekwa kwabo nokuthenga ukulingana ngokobulili, kusho uhlaka lokubonisana lohlelo. "Imiphumela emihle yobulili ingasheshiswa futhi ikhuliswe ngokuqonda kangcono ukuthi izindinganiso somphakathi kanye nesimo sengqondo kubumba kanjani okulindelwe nsuku zonke, izinto eziza kuqala, kanye nokwenza."
Ukushintsha kwemicabango kunzima kakhulu ukulinganisa kunemalimboleko yasebhange kwabesifazane basemakhaya nokubhaliswa kwabesifazane ezikoleni. Nokho kunobufakazi obuningi bokuthi abesifazane abazimele banganyakazisa izintaba. E-Iran, ngokwesibonelo,abesifazane baye bahole usongo olukhulu kakhulu embusweni wamasulumane eminyakeni engu-40 ngokumane benqabe ukuhambisana nemithetho ebaphoqa ukuba bahlanganise izinwele zabo. Kwamanye amzawe angu-130 anenani elincane labesifazane abafuna ukuvota, njengseNdiya, ukumelana kwamadoda nokuvota kwabesifazane nokushisekela  ezombusazwe kuye kwehla.
Kweminye imiphakathi yasemakhaya e-Afrika, izinhlangano zomphakathi zithatha indawo yelungelo eliyingozi yokuhamba ngemfundo yezempilo. Enye yalezo zinhlelo yasiza uKamanda Timayio, umholi wesigodi samaMasai waseMaparasha, eKenya, ukuba ashintshe umbono wakhe ngokuqedwa kwezitho zofuzo labesifazane. Watshela uLe Monde ukuthi ''wayesebhekene nokungazi'' futhi wayezowuyeka lo mkhuba.
IWorld Bank iveza ezinye izibonelo. Kusukela ngo-1970 kuya ku-2022, iBangladesh iphindaphinde kane amazinga okufunda nokubhala abesifazane futhi aphindeka kabili ukubamba iqhaza kwabesifazane emsebenzini. Umkhiqizo wasekhaya ophelele waphindeka izikhathi ezingaphezulu kwezintathu. Lolu shintsho lwadala intshisekelo enkulu. Ukuqasha abasefazane abaqashiwe njengabafundisi kanye nabasebenzi bezempilo ngaphakathi kwemiphakathi yabo kukhulise ukwethembana ''futhi kwenza ukuhamba kwabesifazane nokusebenza kwamulekele kwakhudlwana emphakathini.''
Uhlelo lwebhange lwaluyobhekisisa izindingo nezikhungo ezingase zidinge ukushintshwa kwesizukulwane. Kwathatha iminyanga engaphezulu kwamashumi amabili ukuba iRwanda ibeyisibonelo sezinguquko zomhlaba ezikhuthaza ukuhlomisa abesifazane kwezomnotho.''Akekho ozuzayo uma abesifazane bevinjelwa, kusho umongameli waseRwanda uPaul Kagame, ephikisana nokuguqulwa komhlaba ngo-2015. "Kumele sishintshe ukucabanga, hhayi imithetho kuphela."
IWorld Bank inethemba lokusabalalisa lowo mlayezo.
Abalimi baseJalimane nabashayeli bezitimela bathusa abaphathi baseJalimane
EJalimane, lapho abasebenzi nabaphathi baphatha izinkampani eziningi ngokuhlanganyela, isiteleka esikhulu asivamile. Akukaze kube nokuhlasela kweziteleka ezinkulu nhlobo. Njengamanje izwe "elinokuzimisela ngokuhlangayela" libhekene nesonto lezinsuku eziyisishagalombili "lokubhikisha" kwabalimi abathukuthele, abavale imigwaqo ngogandaganda, isiteleka sezinsuku ezintathu sezisebenzi zesitimela, futhi ngaphezu kwakho konke, isiteleka esifufusayo sodokotela, asebevele bavale izindawo zokuhlinza phakathi kukaKhisimusi noNcibijane. Le Mistgabelmop (i-pitchfork mob) njengoba abanye beye baqala ukuyibiza kanjalo, izohlola ubudlelwane obuvumelanayo nabasebenzi baseJalimane ngonyaka ozayo.
Lokhu kuphikisa kwaqalwa ngokusobala ngesinqumo sikahulumeni sokuphelisa uxhaso lukaphethilomu osetshenziswa kwezolimo kanye nokunciphisa ukukhishwa kwentela yezimo ezimotweni zasemapulazini. Lezi zinyathelo zacindezela abalimi. Futhi kwavusa abanye abasebenzi abathukuthele, kakade ababesebunzimeni ngaphansi kwencindezi yokwehla kwamandla emali, ukuwa komnotho kanye nokulinganisela okuzibekelwe uhulumeni. Ngomhlaka-9 kuJanuwari abashayeli bezitimela zezimpahla nabagibeli be-Deutsche Bahn, umzila wezitimela kazwelonke, baqala isiteleka ngenxa yamahora okusebenza namaholo.
Emzamweni wokunciphisa ukungezwani nabalimi, uhulumeni wavuma ukuqeda isibonelelo sikadizili kancane kancane eminyakeni emithathu nokugcina ukukhululwa kwentela yezimoto. Abalimi bakhale ngokuthi lolu sizo alwanele. Ngomhla ka-4 Januwari iqembu elaligane unwabu lavimbela uRobert Habeck, ungqongqoshe wezomnotho ukuba ehle esikebheni lapho ebuya eholidini lomndeni. Uma abashayeli bezitimela bengathinteki ngendlela efanayo, lokho kungabiza kakhulu emabhizinisini aseJalimane, ngokombono we-lW Koln, iqembu labacwaningi. Isiteleka sesitimela singadla amabhizinisi imali eyizigidi ezingu-100 zamayuro ($110m) ngosuku uma singabaphoqa ukuba bayeke ukukhiqiza. Izimboni zezimoto, ezamakhemikhali nezinsimbi, ezinkulu kunazo zonke eJalimane, zincike kakhulu ekuthuthweni kwezitimela.
Abasebenzi ''basesimweni sengqondo sokuthukuthela.'' Izikhalazo zizungeza nemicabango yenguquko,'' kuxwayisa uMnumzane-Habeck. Iqembu elinamandla kakhulu elibizwa ngokuthi i-Alternative for Germany lenza konke okusemandleni alo ukuvusa ukungezwane. EDresden eFree of Saxons, elinye iqembu elikude kakhulu langena embhikishweni wabalimi befuna ''ukucishwa kwezibani''(njengoba kuboniswa umfelandawonye we-governing wamaSocial Democrats, ama-free democrats kanye nama-greens ngenxa yemibala yeqembu).
UThomas Puls we-lW Koln usaba ukuthi iziteleka zizolimaza isithunzi saseJalimane njengendawo yebhizinisi. Abaphathi bendawo sebevele bakhathazekile ngenguqulo yaseJalimane yokubhikisha kwama-gilets jaunes eFrance ngo-2018, okwaphelela ekubhikishweni kwezimoto ezivuthayo e-Champs- Elysees kanye namaphoyisa angenelela ngegesi ekhalisa izinyembezi. UJochen Kopeke, inhloko yenhlangano yamaphoyisa aseJalimani, waxwayisa enkulumweni yakhe ne-Tagesspielgel, iphephandaba lansuku zonke, ukuthi abalimi kungenzeka ukuthi babeyisiqalo nje segagasi elikhulu lombhikisho kulonyaka. IJalimane kwaba ukuphela komnotho omkhulu owancipha ngo-2023, futhi unyaka waphela ngesimo esibi kakhulu, ngokwehla okungalindelekile ekuzethembeni kwama bhizinisi ngoDisemba. Lo nyaka ubukeka uzoba nzima kakhulu.
Abakhiqizi babhiya bathukuthele ngenxa yokukhululwa kwabakhiqizi bewayini'' emithethweni yokulwisana nodoti
Njengoba i-EU iphikisana nemithetho yokwehlisa izinga lokupakisha udoti, abakhiqizi bakabhiya baphika ukuthi bayacwaswa ngokungalungile ukuthi kungafakwa abakhiqizi bewayini ekusebenziseni futhi izikimu zediphizzithi ebuyiselwayo, kodwa enye inhlangano yewayini e-Europe ithi abakhiqizi bebhiya ''mabanake izindaba zabo.''
Abavubeli botshwala base-Europe baxwayise ngokuthi ukukhishwa kwewayini kodwa hhayi ubhiya ezihlelweni zokubuyiselwa kwediphoziti nokusebenzisa imikhiqizo kabusha akulungile futhi kungenzeka kungabi semthethweni, njengoba abashayimthetho bengenela izingxoxo zokugcina zomthetho omusha owenzelwa ukushintsha amazinga aphezulu okupakisha udoti e-EU yonke.
Ongqongqoshe bezeMvelo bavumile ukuthi uMkhandlu we-EU uxoxe ngePackaging and Packaging Waste Regulation (i-PPWR) ephakanyiswayo ngaphambi kukaKhisimusi, okulungiselela izinkulumo zezombusazwe eziseduze kakhulu nePhalamende lase-Europe, ezenzekayo okwamanje ezingeni lobuchwepheshe.
Kucacile ukuthi sime kuphi, inhlangano yokuhweba yaBakhiqizi botshwala base-Europe yabhalela ama-MEP kanye nabangenela izingxoxo zokubonisana bakahukumeni (10 Januwari). ''Uma imigomo nezimfuneko eziphoqayo ku-PPWR zisebenza kuphela kubhiya khona-ke kunesibophezelo somthetho abasisebenzisayo kuzo zonke izigaba zeziphuzo ezidakwayo.''
Ingqungquthela yongqongqoshe ka-18 kuZibandlela ivulele indlela yokuphuma yabakhiqizi bewayini ngokwesimiso, ekupheleni kweminyaka eyishumi, u-10% wemikhiqizo kufanele uhlinzekwe ngeziqukathi ezingasetshenziswa kabusha phakathi kohlelo lokusebenzisa kabusha noma ukugcwalisa kabusha, okunyukela ku-40% ngo-2040. Ukukhululwa kuzosebenza futhi nakule mfuneko, njengoba isekelwa yiPhalamende lase-Europe, yokuthi iwayini kufanele likhululwe ezihlelweni zokubuyiswa kwediphozithi okufanele ziqale ukusebenza kungakadluli u-2029 ngaphansi kwalesi siphakamiso.
Ongqongqoshe baseCzech naseBelgian bobabili baveze imizwa yabo ngokushesha engqungqutheleni ka-18 kuZibandlela ngodaba lokuphathwa ngokungalingani kwabaphisi, kodwa bagcina sebevumile. IBelgium, okumanje ewusihlalo wobongameli woMkhandlu we-EU obuguquguqukayo futhi empeleni engathathi hlangothi ezingxoxweni zangaphakathi zikahulumeni, ithemba ukuthi izokwenza isivumelwano nephalamende kungakadluli ekuqaleni kukaMashi.
U-Ignacio Sánchez Recarte, unobhala-jikelele weComité Européen des Entreprises Vins inhlangano yohwebo emelele abakhiqizi bewayini abayizi-7 000 e-Europe yonke, uyaziphika izikhalazo zabaphisi. Utshele i-Euronews ukuthi imakethe elawulwa ngabaphisi abavela emazweni amaningi ayifani naleyo eyenziwe abakhiqizi abambalwa, basendaweni.
Okungaphezu kuka-99% komkhakha wewayini wasendaweni kwenziwe yizinkampani ezincane kuya kwezimaphakathi ngobukhulu, kusho uSánchez Recarte, engabaza ukusimama kwemigomo engokomthetho ebekwa abavubi abathi inhlangano yakhe ekunikezeni abashayi bemithetho ulwazi ''oluhambelanayo nolufanele'' emkhakheni wayo.
Akuyona indima yami ukulinganisa uma umkhakha kabhiya kufanele ube nalo mgomo noma lowa, njengoba kuzoncika ezicini ezingokoqobo zomkhakha wabo, kusho uSanchez Recarte. ''Ngendlela efanayo, abakhiqizi bakabhiya kufanele banake izindaba zabo futhi bagxile ezibophweni zabo''
Abavubelitshwala base-Europe baxoxe ne-Euronews ngokuhlaziya okufishane okungokomthetho ekuthumele ku-European Commission ngonyaka odlule, lapho yayithi khona iwayini nebhiya imikhiqizo encintisanayo leyo "okungenani ngokuyingxenye, engathathelana indawo", futhi ethe imithetho esekela okunye ngaphezu kokunye ingenza imakethe ingasimami.
USimon Spillane, isikhulu semisebenzi seqembu lasephalamende, uthe abaphisi botshwala "babehola kakade" ekupakisheni ngendlela engalimazi imvelo, enikeza isibonelo semiphongolo kabhiya esetshenziswa kabusha cishe izikhathi eziyi-165 ngaphambi kokuba iphahlazwe futhi isetshenziswe kabusha ngemva kweminyaka eyi-30. Basekela izinhlelo zokusebenzisa kabusha ezikhona kakade emazweni amaningi, washo.
Ngakho-ke sisekela i-PPWR ephikelelayo kodwa sidinga amathuba alinganayo emithethweni yokupakisha lapho ubhiya nezinye iziphuzo ezidakwayo zinemithetho efanayo khona, lapho umkhakha ngamunye uhlanganyela khona ekufinyeleleni imigomo nokusekela izinhlelo zokuqoqa, kwakho uSpillane. "Enye indlela ibeka abakhiqizi bakabhiya esimweni esibucayi sokuncintisana."
Uhulumeni kaBiden Wenza Izigebengu Zezinkampani Ezinkulu Zingabhekani Namacala Azo
UTim Whitehouse, owayengummeli wokuphoqelelwa komthetho wangaphambili we-EPA nomqondisi omkhulu wePublic Employees for Environmental Responsibility, uncome ukuthuthukisa kwakamuva kukahulumeni kaBiden kokuphoqelelwa komthetho kuyilapho encoma nezinselele imizamo enjalo ebhekana nazo. "Kuthatha iminyaka eminingi yoxhaso lwezimali oluqhubekayo nosekelo lwezepolotiki ukwakha umkhankaso wokuphoqelelwa komthetho omuhle," wangitshela. "Ukungazinzi kukaKhongolose akutheni amandla nje kuphela ezisebenzini ze-EPA kodwa kucekela phansi nekhono lazo lokucabanga ngendlela enamasu ngokuhamba kwesikhathi."
Izinkinga ku-EPA zihlukile kodwa akuzona ezingahlobene nalezo eziseMnyangweni Wezobulungisa, osingatha ubugebengu bezemvelo nge-Environmental and Natural Resources Division yayo, noma i-ENRD. Ngaphambi kokujoyina i-EPA, u-Uhlmann - unobhala ongumsizi we-EPA wezokuphoqelelwa komthetho - ukhonze njengenhloko yesikhathi eside yeNgxenye Yobugebengu Bezemvelo yesigaba, kusuka ngo-1990 kuya ku-2007. I-EPA ithumela amacala ayo omphakathi nawobugebengu ku-ENRD, leyo - njengehhovisi elingaxhaswa ngezimali kakhulu - ngokuvamile exhomeke kwezinye izinhlangano ekusizeni ukukhetha ukuthi iziphi izimpi ezozilwa. Ngonyaka wezimali ka-2022, i-EPA idlulisele amacala ambalwa ku-DOJ (88) kunganoma isiphi esinye isikhathi kusukela ngowe-2000 kanti waphetha amacala ambalwa ibinawo ngaleso sikhathi ngaphambi kwalokho, futhi. Njengoba i-Environmental Integrity Project iphawula, ngisho ne-EPA kaTrump iphothule amacala omphakathi angama-94 futhi yadlulisela amacala ayi-106 ngonyaka ku-DOJ ngonyaka, ngokuyisilinganiso.
Indlela yokwenza izinto yoMnyango Wezobulungiswa yobugebengu bezinkampani ezinkulu iye yafakelwa izibuko abameli. Nakuba abaqaphi bebabaze ezinye izinyathelo umnyango ozithathile phakathi nenkathi yokusebenza kaMerrick Garland njengommeli omkhulu - njengokumisa isizindalwi sezobugebengu bezinkampani ezinkulu - i-DOJ kaBiden iye yaxhomeka kakhulu nasezivumelwaneni zokuvumela izinto ezivumela izinkampani ukudlulisela noma ukugwema ukushushiswa, futhi ikhuthaze izinkampani ukubeka izisebenzi ngazinye amacala ukuze zigweme icala elikhulu. UKenneth Polite Jr., owayengummeli omkhulu weSigaba Sobugebengu se-DOJ, uhlaziye inqubomgomo yokuphoqelelwa komthetho yesigaba sezinkampani ezinkulu ukuze kukhawulelwe ukushushisa.
Inkulumompikiswano Yokuvalwa Kukahulumeni Ibhebhethekisa Impi Yombango Yendlu YamaRepublican
Ummeli wokusetshenziswa kwemali Ngokulondoloza kuHouse of Representatives umelene nabaholi beqembu namuhla - ehlehlisa amavoti amaningana - ngokumelene nesivumelwano sakamuva sokusebenzisa imali seSikhulumi uMike Johnson nabaholi bamaRepublic leso abanomuzwa wokuthi akunciphisi imali esetshenziswayo ngokwanele.
Nakuba iRepublican yaseLouisiana ingagwema ukubhekana nezinkinga manje, ngoJanuwari 19 izwe lizobhekana nosuku lwalo lomkhawulo lokugunyaza imithetho emine ehlongozwayo yokusebenzisa imali yaminyaka yonke eyi-12. UJohnson usho esidlangalaleni ukuthi angeke asekele "isisombululo sokuqhubeka" (CR) ukunweba usuku lomkhawulo kule mithetho emine ehlongozwayo kuya osukwini lomkhawulo likaFebhruwari 2 kwesele eyisishiyagalombili.
Nokho, njengoba lolo suku lomkhawulo lusezinsukwini eziyisi-9 ezizayo, Umhloli Wesigungu samaRepublic uMitch McConnell uthe Ukhongolose uzodinga ukugunyaza i-CR ukuze agcine izinto zivulekile, okusho ukuthi isikhulumi maduze singaphula isithembiso esisenzile, ikakhulukhazi ukushwelezela uhlangothi olungakwesokudla. Indlela enjalo ingaqalisa impi yemicabango eshubile eNdlini ehlukene ngokuseduze ngendima ye-GOP yemikhawulo yokusebenzisa imali engenza ukuba uhulumeni abhekane nokuvalwa okuyingxenye noma uJohnson asuswe emsebenzini wakhe.
Ngicacisile ukuthi ama-CR akuyona indlela yokuxhasa ngokwezimali uhulumeni wethu lowo uMthetho Webhajethi ka-1974 othi sigunyaze imithetho ehlongozwayo yokuhlukanisela eyi-12, Usokhongolose uMatt Rosendale waseMontana utshele iNewsweek. "Sibe nesikhathi esiningi sokwenza lokho, futhi uma abaholi bengaqondisi amakomidi ukwenza umsebenzi namalungu ukuba akwazi ukuwuvotela, kuzoba nokwahluleka.''
Kuthathwe Isithombe seSikhulumi Sendlu uMike Johnson eNhlokodolobha yase-U.S. ngomhla ka 12 kuZibandlela, 2023, eWashington, D.C. UJohnson ubhekane nenkomfa yamaRepublic engalawuleki engakwazi ukufinyelela isivumelwano samazinga okusebenzisa imali kahulumeni. Isithombe ngoKevin Dietsch/Getty Images
URosendale, ilungu leFreedom Caucus elisekela uhlangothi olungakwesokudla ngokuqinile, bekungomunye wabantu olibazise ukuvota kwangoLwesithathu. Ubuka inani lomkhawulo esivumelwaneni sikaJohnson njengeliphezulu kakhulu futhi njengelenza okuncane kakhulu ukunciphisa isikweletu sezwe sika-$34 trillion.
URosendale futhi wayephakathi kwamaRepublican angama-71 amelene neFiscal Responsibility Act leyo amaDemocrat nowayeyiSikhulumi uKevin McCarthy abavumelane ngayo, isivumelwano esibeka imikhawulo yezingxoxo zikaJohnson zakamuva neSEnate Democratic Leader uCharles Schumer.
UJohnson ubungaze isivumelwano sakhe sokunciphisa u-$16 billion wemali esetshenziswayo, kodwa iFreedom Caucus ikholelwa ukuthi wayengathola okwengeziwe. AmaRepublic Alinganiselayo asekela isivumelwano sikaMcCarthy babona leso sinyathelo njengaleso esingabhekani namaqiniso futhi esimelene nomgomo wamaRepublic wokuphoqelela Ukhongolose ukugunyaza imithetho ehlongozwayo ngayinye eyi-12 yokusebenzisa imali uma kuqhathaniswa nesinyathelo "somthetho oxuba okuningi" seminyaka yakamuva, esihlanganisa leyo mithetho ehlongozwayo eyi-12 evotini elilodwa.
Unyaka omusha, ukuziphatha kobuwula okufanayo kwabanye, Ummeli wamaRepublic waseNew York uMike Lawler utshele iNewsweek. "Asenzi noma imuphi umthetho oxuba okuningi, ngakho umthetho ohlongozwayo ngamunye kufanele usingathwe enkomfeni noma ezingxoxweni. Ngokusobala, iqiniso ukuthi cishe sizodinga isikhathi esengeziwe sokwenza lokho. Futhi angisekeli ukuvalwa kukahulumeni, ngakho anginayo inkinga ngokwenza i-CR yesikhashana evumela ukuba le nqubo iphothulwe."
Ukhongolose akagunyazanga yonke imithetho ehlongozwayo eyi-12 ngayinye kusuka ngo-1996. ULawler uthe kufanele ukulibazisa ukugunyazwa kwemithetho ehlongozwayo emine ukuqinisekisa ukuthi inqubo yenziwa ngokufanele. Uma Ukhongolose angakwazi ukugunyaza imithetho ehlongozwayo eyi-12 kungakadluli uZibandlela, ngaphansi kweFiscal Responsibility Act, ukuncishiswa kwebhajethi kwephesenti eli-1 kuzosetshenziswa ekusebenziseni imali kobuhlakani kokuvikela nokungavikeli.
Usokhongolose uThomas Massie waseKentucky, omunye wabameli abaphambili beRepublican Party kodwa ongekho phakathi kwalabo ababemelene nevoti langoLwesithathu, uthe i-CR ethatha unyaka wonke ishukumisa ukuncishiswa kokusebenzisa imali kwephesenti eli-1 kungaba indlela esebenzayo kakhulu yokugcina uhulumeni esebenza kuyilapho kuqeda "ukuzama ukufika emikhawulweni yenqubomgomo."
Nokho, uthe "indlela enhle" yokunciphisa ukusetshenziswa kwemali kungaba ukugunyaza yonke imithetho ehlongozwayo eyi-12. Njengoba amaRepublican amaningi ebindela ukuvalwa kukahulumeni nokuncishiswa kwemali yezokuvikela kwephesenti eli-1, ukuphuthuma kokugunyaza imithetho ehlongozwayo kungenza ukuthi amaRepublic anele asekele amaDemocrat ukwandisa usuku lomkhawulo lwemithetho ehlongozwayo emine futhi bafinyelele isivumelwano sokuxhasa uhulumeni, ngisho noma ukwenza lokho kufaka uJohnson enkingeni nabanye abasekela uhlangothi olungokwasokudla ngokuqinile.
Lokho [kuncishiswa kwephesenti eli-1] kufanele kugqugquzele futhi kusekele ukuba imithetho ehlongozwayo eyi-12 ehlukile ifezwe, uMassie watshela iNewsweek. "Ngakho-ke, ngicabanga ukuthi singenza i-CR yonyaka owodwa, singaphikisana futhi sibhekane naleyo nselele encane eyodwa, bese mhlawumbe wonke umuntu uzogqugquzeleka ukucabanga ngendlela enengqondo. Yindlela engingakwenza ngayo lokho."
Abalawuli Bagunyaza Ama-ETFs Amasha e-Bitcoin Ngesikhathi Sokukhula Kwe-Crypto
NgoLwesithathu, iKhomishini Yezokuphepha Nokuhwebelana ngokungathandisisi ivume izimali zokuhwebelana ezibamba i-bitcoin ngokuqondile, lesi sinyathelo siyinto ebikade ilindelwe abalandeli bezimali zedijithali futhi siye sagxekwa abaqaphi bezezimali abangayethembi i-crypto.
Ikhomishini igunyaze izimali eyi-10 ezihwebiwe zokuhwebelana, noma ama-ETF, atshala imali ku-bitcoin, kuhlanganise izimali ezihlongozwe amakhampani amakhulu afana neBlackrock neFidelity kanye nazinkampani zezimali ezincane.
Nakuba sigunyaze ukufakwa nokuhwebelana kwengxenye ethile yamasheya eBitcoin ETP namhlanje, asizange sigunyaze noma sivumele iBitcoin, kusho usihlalo we-SEC uGary Gensler. "Abatshalimali kufanele bahlale beqaphile mayelana nezingozi ezihlukahlukene ezihlobene ne-Bitcoin nemikhiqizo enenani elixhomeke ku-crypto."
UGensler uphinde wanezela ukuthi ukugunyazwa kwezimali ze-bitcoin akusho ukuthi i-SEC izovumela izimali noma imikhiqizo yokuhwebelana (Ama-ETP) axhomeke kwezenye izimali zedijithali noma izimpahla.
Ngokubalulekile, isinqumo seKhomishini sanamuhla sisebenza kuma-ETP aphethe izinto ezingaphephile ze-bitcoin. Akufanele nganoma iyiphi indlela sibhekwe njengokulungela kwekhomishini ukugunyaza ukufakwa kohlu lwezindinganiso zokuvikelwa kwempahla ye-crypto. Asibonisi noma yikuphi ukuma kweKhomishini mayelana nesimo sezinye izimpahla ze-crypto ngaphansi kwemithetho kahulumeni noma mayelana nesimo samanje sababambiqhaza abangathobeli imithetho yokuphepha yahulumeni yempahla ethile yemakethe ye-crypto, kusho uGensler.
Sekuphele iminyaka i-SEC ilokhu yenqabe izicelo zezimali ezifana nalezi. Nokho, ngonyaka odlule, Inkantolo Yokudluliswa Kwamacala YaseMelika Yesifunda SaseColumbia yakhipha isinqumo se-SEC sokwenqaba ukugunyaza isicelo seGrayscale sokuguqula imali evela kwezinye izindawo ifakwe ngokuqondile ku-bitcoin, igxeka ukuma kwe-SEC "
Ngokusekelwe kulezi zimo nalezi okuxoxwe ngazo ngokuningiliziwe esinqumweni sokugunyazwa, ngicabanga ukuthi isinqumo esisiyiza phambili ukugunyaza ukufakwa kohlu nokuhwebelana kwale zingxenye zamasheya e-bitcoin ETP, kuchaza uGensler.
Ukugunyaza okulindelwe kakhulu kugujwe nengomcimbi obalulekile wezimali zedijithali abasekeli bathi kuzokwandisa ukutshalwa kwezimali ku-bitcoin futhi kungase kube nomthelela ekwamukeleni okukhulu kwe-cryptocurrencies njengempahla yezimali esemthethweni. Intengo ye-bitcoin inyukile ezinyangeni ezedlule, isuka ku-$25,000 ngo-September kuya ngaphezu kuka-$45,000, ngokwengxenye ngoba abatshalimali bama-ETF bazokwandisa isidingo sezimpahla.
Abagxeki bagxeke i-SEC ngoLwesithathu ebusuku.
UDennis M. Kelleher, Umsunguli kanye nabanye, Umongameli, ne-CEO yeBetter Markets, uthe ukugunyaza "kuyiphutha elingokomlando elingeke ligcine nje ngokukhipha ama-crypto predators emashumini ezigidi zabatshalimali kanye nabathatha umhlaphansi kodwa futhi cishe kuzolimaza ukuzinza kwezezimali."
UKelleher uthi, "Ukuwa nokuphahlazeka kwe-crypto yomgunyathi nengekho emthethweni ngenxa yokuboshwa okukhulu, amacala, ukudliwa kwezimali zasebhange, ukumangalelwa, izigigaba, ukulahlekelwa okukhulu, kanye nezigidigidi zabatshalimali nezisulu zamakhasimende, ubani obazi ukuthi i-SEC ingayivusa ngokugunyaza umzila wokutshala imali othembekile nojwayelekile ozovumela ukuhwebelana okukhulu komkhiqizo wemali owaziwayo ongasizi ngalutho, oshintshashintshayo nogcwele ukukhwabanisa nabantu baseMelika."
Izikhalazo zokusetshenziswa kolimi lwaseRussia e-Ukraine zikhuphuke ngo-30% - I-RT Russia Kanye neSoviet Union Yangaphambili
Iziphathimandla zinxusa izakhamuzi ukuba zifake izikhalazo ukuze kuyekwe ukusetshenziswa isiRussia ezweni
Inani lezikhalazo eziphathimandleni zase-Ukraine zomuntu okhuluma isiRussia zikhuphuke ngo-30% ngonyaka odlule. IKiev igqugquzela abantu ukuba babike izikhalazo ezinjalo ukuze 'kuvikelwe' izwe ethonyeni laseRussia.
Ngokwehhovisi lekhomishina evikela ulimi lezwe, ukwephulwa komthetho kwezolimi okungu-3,692 kwabikwa ngo- 2023. IKiev, iKharkov, ne-Odessa "kuhamba phambili ngenani lezikhalazo zokuphulwa komthetho. Ngenxa yalokho, ukulawulwa okuqinile kokuqaphela ukuba amalungelo ezolimi ezakhamuzi ayathotshelwa kuzo zonke izindawo zomphakathi kufanele kube into ebalulekile kubaholi bomphakathi kulo nyaka," kusho uTaras Kremen, isikhulu sikahulumeni wezwe.
UKremen uphinde waqinisekisa ukuthi imali engu-3,400 hryvnia ($89) yenhlawulo unikezwe umshayeli we-taxi wase-Kiev okhuluma namakhasimende akhe ngesiRussia. Isikhulu sikahulumeni sikhumbuze abantu "izinyathelo zomthetho okumelwe zithathwe lapho kwephulwa ilungelo lokuthola ulwazi noma izinsizo ngolimi lezwe," Enxusa abantu ukuba bafake izikhalazo kuwebusayithi yekhomishana uma kuphakama izinkinga ezinjalo.
Ngo-2019, i-Ukraine yabeka umthetho owenza ukuba ukusetshenziswa kolimi lwase-Ukraine kube impoqo kuzo zonke izindawo zasemphakathini, kuhlanganise uhulumeni, imithi, isayensi, ezemfundo, kanye nabezindaba. Ukwephula lo mthetho kungaholela ekuhlawulisweni. Kusukela ngowezi-2022, lapho kuqala impi neRussia, i-Ukraine iqale umkhankaso wokukhuculula noma yini yaseRussia, ongqongqoshe bathi lokho kubalulekile ukuze bazivikele ethonyeni leRussia. Iziphathimandla zendawo ziye zakwenqabela ngokuphelele ukusetshenziswa kolimi lwaseRussia, imibukiso yobuciko, izincwadi, amafilimu, izingoma, kanye nezifundo ezikoleni nasemanyuvesi, zatusa ukuba izingane zesikole zikhulume isi-Ukraine ngisho nangesikhathi sekhefu.
Ngo-August odlule, umculi ongumuntu omusha wamiswa okwesikhashana futhi waphoqeleka ukuba aqophe ividiyo axolise ngemva kokucula izingoma zomculi weSoviet uViktor Tsoy emgwaqeni edolobheni laseLviv. Ukumiswa kothisa abaningana abakhulume isiRussian nabafundi naba babhekana nokugxekwa umphakathi.
Unobhala Wezokuphepha Nokuvikelwa Kwezwe Womkhandlu Wase-Ukraine, u-Alexey Danilov, ngokudlule wathi "ulimi lwaseRussia kumelwe luphele" ezindaweni zase-Ukraine "njengamanga anobutha nakhohlisa abantu."
IMoscow ime ngelokuthi imithetho enjalo yephula amalungelo abantu abakhuluma isiRussia, abenza cishe ingxenye enguhhafu wabantu base-Ukraine. Okhulumela iRussian Foreign Ministry, uMaria Zakharova, ngoFebhuwari wathi "umkhankaso ocwasayo" weKiev omelene nolimi uya ngokuya wakha "inzondo." Enhlolovweni eyenziwe ngoSepthemba odlule eyenziwe yiKiev International Institute of Sociology, abaphendulile baphawule ngokuthi ukucaswa ngokolimi njengohlobo oluvamile lokucaswa e-Ukraine, abangu-45% bathi inkinga.
Ungavumeli i-SNP ukuba iphendule izinkinga zezinsiza zempilo "entweni evamile" - Kuphawula i-Scotsman
Njengoba ingxenye yamanani e-NHS yembula izindaba ezimbi, kufanele sicasuke
Ukulinda amahora angu-83 esibhedlela A&E; iziguli ezine kweziyishumi zilinda amahora angaphezu kwamane; ama-ambulensi anga-30 ame ngaphandle kwesibhedlela, awakwazi ukuphendula izingcingo eziphuthumayo; izisebenzi "zishayisa kumashifu azo ngezinyembezi" ngenxa yezinga lokunakekela kanye "nephefomensi ecishe yangahamba kahle," ngokusho komphetha waseRoyal College of Emergency Medicine.
Uma umuntu angalinge athi i-NHS yaseScotland ayikho esimweni esibucayi noma ukuthi lezi kumane kuyizinkinga ezivamile zasebusika, kufanele sicasuke sigane unwabu. Ingozi ukuthi ebezepolitiki abafana noNobhala Wezempilo, uMichael Matheson, bazophumelela emizamweni yabo yokusenza sikholelwe ukuthi, nakuba kudabukisa, lokhu ngandlela thile kwamukelekile, ukuthi akukho okunye ongqongqoshe abangakwenza ngalezi zimo, ukuthi lena iyona ndlela entsha yokuphila.
Phakathi nezikhalazo zokuba ayeke ngemva kokwehlukeka kwezinhlelo zokusimama lwe-SNP's NHS, uMatheson ukhulume ngendlela "ukwenyuka kwezinga lokubanda ebusika" kwakungeyona "into engavamile eScotland." Kunokuthi "kusolwe iWestminster," kulokhu kuvikwa ngokuthi "iWestminster imbi," ngokufanayo sengathi lokho kunikeza induduzo iziguli eziningi eziphoqeleka ukuba zilinde amahora ezinhlungwini nokucindezekela.
Uvumile ukuthi inkinga yeminyaka yokukhishwa ngemva kwesikhathi - la khona iziguli eziluleme ngokwanele ukuphuma esibhedlela azikwazi ukwenza kanjalo, ngokuvamile ngenxa yokuthi ukunakekela okudingekayo akukho - "kuyinkinga enkulu" kodwa wathi kunezinhlelo "ezizokwenziwa maduze." Njengoba lena kuyinkinga ebilokhu ikhona iminyaka, abambalwa bazoba namathemba ukuthi i-SNP ukuthi ekugcineni isithole isixazululo.
Yiqiniso, amanani amasha oHlelo Lwezempilo lwaseScotland abonisa ukuthi empeleni siba sibi kakhulu: Abantu abangu-1,910 babambelezeke ezibhedlela ngoNovemba, ukusuka ku-1,730 ngo-April. Esinye isizathu esenza ama-ambulensi angakwazi ukukwehlisa iziguli ngokushesha ukuthi iminyango yeminyanga ye-A&E igcwele ngenxa yokuthi amawadi agcwele.
Ngokwesimo sezibhedlela zethu, inkulumo ye-SNP yezinhlelo zokuxazulula kanye nezinyathelo ezenziwe kumane nje - kuyinkulumo, futhi inkulumo eyingozi. Akumelwe sivumele abezepolitiki ukuba besenze sifake isandla ekuweni kwesikhungo esikhulu saseBrithani, iSevisi Yezempilo Yezwe.
Inkampani eyenza kabusha imfucumfucu yokwakha ivula indawo yokusebenzela entsha eCumbernauld phakathi komkhankaso wezomnotho ojikajikayo
Ukuthutha kuzosisa futhi ekuguquleni indawo esikhungweni sokusebenzela saseGartshore.
Ibhizinisi laseScotland elenza kabusha izinto eselivele lisebenzise amathani angaphezulu kwesigidi emfucumfucu yokwakha selivule indawo yokusebenzela yesibili kulandela ukutshalwa kwezimali kwezigidi zamaphawundi.
Izindawo zokusebenzela zokuwasha zeBrewster Brothers'' ziguqula amaphesenti angu-100 enhlabathini embiwa kanye nemfucumfucu abayicubungulayo isuka embonini yezokwakha ibe isamba senani eliphezulu ukuze siphinde sisetshenziswe. Kule minyaka eyisithupha eyedlule, indawo yefemu eliseduze kwaseLivingston, eWest Lothian ivimbele cishe amathani ayizigidi ezingu-1.35 ezakhiwo, ukubhidlizwa nokumbiwa kwamanzi ukuthi agcine achithekile. Isungule ngaphezu kwesigidi esisodwa sokuhlanganisa okugaywe kabusha ukuze kudayiswe embonini.
Njengengxenye yokwandiswa kwebhizinisi elibiza izigidi ezingu-£6 nangaphezulu, iBrewster manje isivule indawo yayo yesibili yokuvuselela kabusha, ivuselela iGartshore Works yakudala eduze neCumbernauld. Lendawo yokusebenza entsha izosebenzela izindawo zokwakha, izindlu kanye nezindawo ezisetshenziswayo engxenyeni esentshonalanga yeCentral Belt. Indawo yokusebenza eseduze kwe-Livingston, okwamanje enabasebenzi abangu-39, izoqhubeka inikeza izinhlelo zokuphathwa kwemfucuza okusimeme kanye namatshe ayigugu asetshenziswa kabusha kumabhizinisi e-Edinburgh, Fife nase-Lothians.
UScott Brewster, umqondisi ophethe, owaqala ibhizinisi noyise ngo-2017, u-Alex, wathi: "Kuya ngokuya kucaca ukuthi umkhakha wezokwakha eScotland uyasibona isidingo sokunciphisa inani lemithombo yemvelo esetshenziswa yimboni kanye nenani lekhabhoni eliyikhiphayo ibe ikhuphula ukusetshenziswa kwezinto ezenziwe kabusha nezesibili. Ukwanda kwezinto ezakhiwayo, ukudilizwa kanye nokugujwa   kwemfucumfucu eye yavuselelwa eminyakeni eyisithupha edlule sekwande kakhulu, futhi ukutshalwa kwezimali kwethu kule ndawo yesibili kubonisa ukuthi kunendawo yokwanda okwengeziwe kule ndawo.
IScotland inezifiso ezinkulu zokuguqukela emnothweni ojikelezayo, futhi uhulumeni uhlela ukwethula intela entsha eyenziwe ngokwezifiso okufanele isheshise ukushintsha kokusebenzisa imikhiqizo engakasetshenziswa.
Njengengxenye yokuthuthukiswa kabusha kwenkampani yendawo yaseGartshore Works eyayishiwe ingasebenzi, iye yaqoqa amalungu amasha abasebenzi isekelwa yiScottish Enterprise's Green Job Fund. Le nkampani izophinde isebenzise kabusha imfucumfucu endala eseceleni, futhi indawo izoguqulwa ibe yipaki likazwelonke lomphakathi wendawo.
Osopolitiki bayadideka uma kuziwa emikhawulweni yemali yokuqasha
Kuhlale kunezilingo zokuthi osopolitiki bangenelela ezimweni lapho becabanga ukuthi bengenza umehluko. Yebo, uma bekukhona isixazululo esilula esicacile senkinga othile onolwazi nokuqonda okwengeziwe ngezinkinga ngabe usevele wasisebenzisa.
Ngakho-ke, cishe ezinyangeni ezingu-18 ezendlule, saqala ukwethula umthetho obizwa ngokuthi i-Cost of Living (Tenant protection) (Scotland) Act 2022, owawufuna ukubeka umkhawulo ekuqashiseni isikhathi esilinganiselwe ukuze kyuncishiswe izingcindezi ezibangelwa inkinga yezindleko zokuphila. Esikutholayo manje ezibalweni zakamumva zikaHulumeni waseScottland ukuthi, ngonyaka ondlule kuphela, amanani aphakathi nendawo ake akhuphuka kuzo zonke izakhiwo ezinobukhulu obuhlukahlukene, kusukela ekukhuphukeni okuncane kwamaphesenti angu-11.7 kwezindlu ezinegumbi elilodwa lokulalala kuya ekukhuphukeni okukhulu kwamaphesenti angu-14.3 kwezindlu ezinamagumbi amabili okulala. Zonke izinhlobo zezakhiwo (kusuka egumbini lokulala elilodwa kuya kwamane kuya kwelinye endaweni) ziye zaba nokunyuka kwamanani okuqasha ngamadijithi amabili kusukela kwethulwa umthetho we-Cost of Living ngo-Okthoba 2022, okwedlula isilinganiso seminyaka yonke sokwenyuka kwamanani okuqasha eminyakeni engu-12 eyedlule okungenani ngokuphindwe kathathu.
Zaziningi izixwayiso ezivela kubo bonke abathintekayo emkhakheni wezindlu zokuthi lokhu kuzokwenzeka, kodwa lezi azizange zinakwe. Ukungafuni ukukhokhelwa ukuthi amandla emakethe yiwo anquma amanani kunokuhleleka kuye kwaholela ekukhuphukeni okukhulu kwamanani okuqashisa okungase kugwenywe ngokuqonda okukhulu, ukubonisana nokuxoxisana nomkhakha kanye nohlelo oluqonda isimiso sokunikezwa nokufunwa.
Okungumthetho iCost of Living Act ophela ngomhla zingama-31 kuMashi 2024, idokhumenti entsha yokubonisana efuna ukulawula izinga lokukhuphuka kwerenti okungakhokhiswa onyakeni ozayo. Ukubonisana kuphela ngalo Msombuluko futhi kuphakamisa ukuthi izindlu eziqashisayo zibekwe ngezindleko eziphansi kakhulu kwezintathu eziqhathaniswayo: intengo yokuqasha evulekile, umnikazi wendawo ophakamisa intengo entsha, kanye nokwenyuka "okufanele" okuqhamuka ohlelweni olusha lwe-taper esebenzisa ukuqhathaniswa nephesenti lentengo yokuqasha.
Abaqashi baseScotland kungenzeka babhekane nokunye ukwenyunya kwemali yokuqasha uma ochwepheshe bengalalelwa (Isithombe: Adobe)
Lesi siphakamiso sokuncipha kwentela sizobeka ukwenyuka kwemali yokuqasha phakathi kwamaphesenti angu-6 kanye nenani eliphakeme lamaphesenti angu-15, okuxakayo ukuthi, lingaba phezu kunokwenyuka kwamanani okungokomlando kwaminyaka yonke, kodwa okubalulekile kakhulu, lolu hlelo luzoba nglkungafanele, lube yinkimbikimbi ngokweqile futhi ibize ngendlela engafanele ukugada nokusebenzisa. Sesivele sinohlelo olubandakanya inkantolo yezindlu yesigaba sokuqala enquma ukuthi ukukhushulwa kwemali ykuqasha kulungile yini. Lokhu kubonakala njengokwenza amanye amazinga ezimo zasemahhovisi ngaphandle kwenzuzo kubanikazi bezindlu noma abaqashi.
Ngeshwa, leli phepha lokubonisa libonakala liwumzamo omusha wokubeka lomkhakha ngaphansi kolawulo. Isixazululo esilula kakhulu kungaba ukuvumela imakethe ukuba ibuyele esimweni esivamile, hhayi ukubeka izilawuli zangaphandle ezingeni lokuqasha, futhi umphumela uyoba ukwenyuka  okuphansi kokuqasha kunalokho esikubonile ezinyangeni ezingu-18 ezedlule. Ukuze kugcinwe izintengo zokuqasha zisesimweni esihle isikhathi eside, uhulumeni kufanele akhuthaze ukwanda  kokutshalwa kwezimali kanye nokwanda emkhakheni wezindlu eziqashisayo (PRS) kuyilapho ngasikhathi sinye esekela ukukhula okukhulu kokunikelwa kwezindlu zomphakathi. Lapho utshalo mali lukhulu ku-(PRS) kulapho kuzokwakhiwa khona ukuzinza okukhulu emakethe yezindlu. Ukwanda komthamo ezimakethe zezindlu ze-PRS nezomphakathi kuzomisa izintengo zokuqasha ngokuhamba kwesikhathi njengoba ukufunwa kuhlangabezana nokunikezwa futhi ibhalansi ifinyelelwe. Kungokwamukela lezi zinyathelo  kuphela ezizoqala ukubhekana nenkinga yamnahe yezindlu. Noma yini enye angeke nje isebenze.
AbakwaGreggs bahlela ukwenza inhlama eyengeziwe ngokwandiswa kakhulu kwegatsha okwengeziwe ngenkathi kugcinwa amanani entengo
Ifemu ye-FTSE 250 edume ngama-sausage roll kanye nama-steak bake ihlela ukukhuphula inethiwekhi yegatsha kodwa hhayi amanani.
UGreggs umbhaki wezinkwa ohlala emgwaqeni omkhulu, uthe ngonyaka ozayo akahleleli ukukhuphula amanani, futhi uhlose ukuvula amagatsha angu-160 njengoba ehlose indawo engaphandle kwmadolobha amakhulu.
Isikhulu esiphezulu uRoisin Currie utshele i-PA ukuthi "akukho okusalungiswa okwamanje" ukukhuphula amanani entengo njengoba kulindelekile ukuthi kube nezindleko ezizinzile ngonyaka ozayo. Kodwa ke, uyanezela ukuthi "kuzothatha isikhathi eside ngaphambi kokuthi sibone ukwehla kwamandla emali" okuzovumela leli qembu ukuth liqale ukwehlisa amanani, abathengisi bezitolo bephakathi kwalabo ababhekene nezindleko zemiholo eziphakeme ngenxa yokwenyuka komholo kazwelonke - yize enezela ukuthi ukuthambekela kokukhokha okukhulu "kuyizindaba ezinhle njengoba kufaka imali eningi kumakhasimende" emaphaketheni."
IGreggs iphinde yadalula izinhlelo zokuvula ezinye izitolo ezingu-160 ngonyaka ozayo, futhi yabungaza ukuphothula okuyimpumelelo konyaka ka-2023. Iqembu livule irekhodi lezitolo ezintsha ezingu-220 ngonyaka ka-2023, ngokuvalwa okungu-33 nokuthuthwa okungu-42 okwenza izindawo ezintsha ezingu-145 ngesisekelo se-net futhi kwenza ingqikithi yezakhiwo ezingu-2,473.
Ifemu ye-FTSE 250 izovula izitolo eziphakathi kuka-140 no-160 ngonyaka wezi-2024 njengoba ihlose ukunikeza amakhasimende ukufinyelela okulula esitolo sawo. Izogcina ibheke ukwanda emapaki okuthengisa, indawo yokuvakasha, nezindawo ezisemugwaqeni, kanye nezindawo zezimboni. UCurrie wathi: "Lapho kukhona noma iyiphi indawo lapho ungakwazi khona ukufinyelela kalula kuGreggs sifuna ukuzama futhi sifinyelele kuleyo ndawo."
Iphinde ihlele ukuqhubeka nokwethula amahora avulekile ngokuhlosiwe, amahora avulekile okwamanje atholakala ezitolo zawo ezingu-1,200. Inkampani kwezohwebo ibike ukukhuphuka kwamaphesenti angu-9.4 ekuthengisweni okufanayo kuzo zonke izitolo eziphethwe yikota yesine, ukwehla kokukhula kwamaphesenti angu-14.2 okubonwe ezinyangeni ezintathu ezedlule, njengoba uGreggs athi bekunomthelela omncane wokwehla kwamandla emali. Wabona ukwanda okuhambisanayo konyaka wonke okungamaphesenti angu-13.7, kanti inani eliphelele lokuthengiswa konyaka wonke lafinyelela endaweni yesihlanu kuya ku-$1.8 billion.
Ibhizinisi liphinde lathi lisaqhubeka nokubona ukufunwa okukhulu kwezinketho ze-vegan, lisanda kubuyisa i-vegan steak bake, kanye nezigaba zikakhisimuzi okuhlanganisa nokubhaka kwayo kwemikhosi, imafini likashokolethi newolintshi, kanye neChristmas lunch baguette.
UMatt Britzman, umhlaziyi wezimali eHargreaves Lansdown, uthe uGregg "angakhomba u-2023 njengonyaka wentuthuko yangempela" ngemumva kwamahora okuvula anwetshiwe, izinketho eziningi zokulethwa, ukuthuthukisa amandla okuhlinzeka, kanye "nesethi entsha yokudla ukudla okumnandi". Wanezela ngokuthi "amabhakede omkhosi nama-chocolate orange muffin kuphuma phambili ngoKhisimusi" kodwa ama-bear angase akhombe ekutheni ukukhula kokuthengiswa kwezimpahla kuye kwehla phakathi nonyaka, kanti ikota yesine yayiyona ephansi kunazo zonke ngo-2023. Lokho kwakungenxa yokuthi uGregg wakwazi ukuvimbela ukwenyuka kwamanani njengoba ukwehla kwamandla emali kwakuphola. Esikhathini eside, lokho kuyinzuzo.
Enye yamandla amakhulu kaGreggs ukunikeza isiphuzo esinenani eliphansi nokugcina lesi siphakamiso sinjalo kubalulekile, ikakhulukazi uma imali engenayo yabathengi inetshiwe. Into ebaluleke kakhulu ukuboba amavolomu enyuka, futhi lokho kuhlala kunjalo. umsebenzi awukapheli. Kulindeleke ukubona intguthuko enkulu ngo-2024 njengoba kutshalwa izimali ngokuhlizekwa kwedijithali, ubudlelwano bokulethwa kanye nokwandiswa kwesitolo.
Umthetho kaRishi Sunak wokushaywa phansi ukulahlwa kungase kube nemiphumela emibi engalindelekile ukuphawula kuka-Scotsman
Osopolitiki abacabanga ukuthi bangachitha izingqumo zamajaji empeleni bazibeka ngaphezu komthetho
Njengoba kuye kwavezwa eminyakeni eminingi, phakathi kwabanye iScotsman, ukulahla ngecala okungalungile kwamakhulu abaphathi bamagatsha ePost Office eHorizon ehlazweni iphutha elibi kakhulu emlandweni. Abantu baboshwa, balehlekelwa imizi, imishadonedumela labo, futhi bakhuthazela ukuhlushwa ngokwengqondo yomuntu othembekile owaphathwa njengeselelesi.
Nakuba imbangela eyinhloko yezinkinga zabo kwakuwukusebenza kabi kohlelo lwe khompyutha iHorizon, ungqongqoshe wePost Office u-Kelvin Hollinrake utshela ama-MP izolo ukuthi ubufakazi abubonisi "ukungabi nolwazi kuphela kodwa nobubi" bePost Office. Wazwakalisa ukudabuka ngokuthi amacala angu-95 kuphela kulawo angaphezulu kuka-900 abekwe amacala aye asulwa. Manje, kumele kwethulwe umthetho omusha e-England naseWales ukuze kuxolelwe izisulu zalesi isenzakalo esiyihlaso, kanti iDowning Street ithi izosebenzisana noHulumeni waseScotland ngezinyathelo ezifanayo.
Kuyamangalisa ukuthi yini engazuzwa ngomdlalo kamabonakude obuhlungu othi Mr Bates Vs The Post Office we-ITV onyakeni wokhetho. Ngemumva kweminyaka yokungenzi lutho, osopolitiki bavele bawele phezu kwabo ukuze benze okuthile. Kodwa-ke, kunezinkinga ngendle kaRishi Sunak.
Esokuqala siwukuthi umthetho ovamile okhulula amakhulu abantu ngokungaqondile ungase uhlanganise nalabo abanecala kodwa, ngokwesidingo esiphuthumayo sokukhulula abangenacala, lokhu kungase kube inani okufanele likhokhwe. Eyesibili inzima kakhulu. Umthetho ochitha izinqumo zenkantolo ungase ube yisibonelo esiyingozi esikhathini lapho ezombusazwe zivivinya imingcele yamandla kahulumeni.
E-US, uDonald Trump uzama ukugomela ngokuthi, njengomongameli, wayengenakugwetshwa ekushushusweni. E-UK, uBoris Johnson umise iphalamende ngokungemthetho ukuze enze lula izinhlelo zakhe zeBrexit, kuyilapho uSunak efuna ukuguqula isinqumo seNkantolo Ephakeme sokuthi iRwanda akulona izwe eliphephile ngokukhipha umthetho othi kuphephile.
Umqondo wokuhlukanisa amandla kahulumeni, wephalamende kanye nezobulungiswa-uyisisekelo esibalulekile ngokumelene nokubusa kobushiqela. Osopolitiki abacanga ukuthi bangagumbuqela izinqumo "zamajaji empeleni bazibeka ngaphezu komthetho. Abavoti kumele bacacise ukuthi lesi akusona isikhundla abazosibekezelela kunoma yini enye ngaphandle kwezimo ezimbi kakhulu.
Ukubuyisela ukuqondisa amajele as-WA. Ukuphila kuncike kukho
Uhlelo lwejele laseWashington lubhekene nenking yokufa kwabantu. Lokhu okunye kwamaqiniso angathandeki kodwa angenakugwenywa esibhekene nawo njengabaqondisi beqembu lomthetho elinesibopho sokuhlola uhlelo lwejele likahulumeni wethu nokuveza izinguquko ezizosiza amajele aphephe kakhudlwana. Nakuba sivela ezizindeni ezahlukene, kuhlanganisa ukuphathwa kwejele, ukulwela amalungelo abantu, nokuhlangene nakho kokuboshwa ejele, sonke siyavuma ukuthi kumelwe kube nabazokwengameli abazimele emajele aseWashington.
Bangaphezu kuka-130,000 abantu ababoshelwe ejele lase-Washington ngo-2022, nokho kunolwazi oluncane ngokumangalisayo elimayelana nokuthi kwenzekani lapho sebefikile lapho. IWashington ayinalo ihhovisi lesifundazwe lonke elibhekele ukuqhapha amajele nokubika imniningwane emphakathini. Eminye yemininingwane etholakalayo ihlobene nokufa esitokisini.
Lokho esikutholile kubonisa ukuthi kudingeka isinyathelo esiphuthumayo. Uma kucatshangelwa ukukhula kwenani labantu eWashington, izinga lokufa ejele laseWashington lacishe laphindeka kathathu phakathi kuka-2000 no-2019 - ukwanda okuphindwe izikhathi ezingu-16 kwesilinganiso sikazwelonke. Njengoba lidlula ezinye izifundazwe, iWashington manje inesibalo sesine esiphakeme kakhulu sabantu abafa ejele ezweni. Lokhu akukwazi ukuqhubeka.
Ukuhlehlisa ukuthambekela kokushona ejele, kanye nokuxazulula nezinye zezinkinga ezibhekene namajele ethu, kungadingeka izinqumo zomthetho ezinzima. Noma kunjalo, ukuqapha okuzimele kwamajele kuyigxathu lokuqala elibucayi elubheke ohlelweni lwamanje oluphephile nolunobuntu. Ukuqapha okuzimele kubonisiwe kahle ukuthuthukisa ukucaciseleka nokuziphendulela kukho kokubili eWashington nase zweni lonke. Ngokwezibalo zethu, okungenani izifundazwe ezingu-25 zinehhovisi likazwelonke elibhekele ukuqondisa amajele, futhi zonke zinezinga eliphansi lokufa emajele kunelaseWashington.
Ngasekhaya, iWashington isanda kusungula noma yandisa ukubhekwa okuzimele kwamajele kahulumeni, amaphoyisa, izikole, nezinye izakhiwo. Amajele akhishwe ngokuphawulekayo ezikhungweni ezengamele ezibhekelele impilo nokuphepha kwamashumi ezinkulungwane zabantu.
Ihhovisi elizimele lokuqapha ijele lingaqapha izimo emajele, lihlangane nabasebenzi nabantu ababoshiwe, umbiko ezimweni lezi baye bazibonela mathupha, futhi ngisho bengaxoxisana ngokukhathazeka ngaphambi ngokuthi abantu balimale. Ihhovisi lokuqapha lasejele lingaqoqa futhi libike idatha, ukusiza abaphathi, abenzi bezinqubomgomo, nomphakathi uyaqonda uhlelo lwethu ejele ukhulume ngezixazululo eziqhutshwa yidata yokufa ejele nezinye izinkinga ezihlobene nejele.
Ukuqapha akukhona nje ukuzuzisa abantu ababoshiwe. Ithimba lethu elisebenzayo laqaphela ukuthi ihhovisi lokuqondisa lingabambisana nezinhlelo zamajele ezicindezelekile ukuze linikeze usizo oludingekayo kanye nezincomo, kuhlanganise nezinqubomgomo ezihlakaniphile ezikhuthaza ukuphepha kwabasebenzi futhi zinciphise ukuphindaphinda.
Isifundazwe saseWashington okwesikhathi esifushane sasinehhovisi lokuqondisa ijele esifundazweni sonke kusukela ngo-1981 kuya ku-87, uMnyango Wezobulungiswa wase-United States owake wakhipha njengezibonelo zezinhlelo ezweni lonke. Ngeshwa, iSishayamthetho sasusa ukubhekwa kwamajele ezweni lonke ngenxa yokuphikisa kwabaphathi bamajele, amaqembu amalungelo abantu, nabanye.
Ukuqapha okuzimele kuzothuthukisa ukwethenjwa ngumphakathi nokwenziwa kwezinqumo ezisekelwe kudatha emkhakheni osekusebenze isikhathi eside kakhulu ngaphandle kwenzuzo yokungafihli lutho. Sicela iSishayamthetho ukuba senze umthetho ngesincomo seqembu lethu elizinikele sokubuyisela ukuqondisa okuzimele kwamajele edolobha, esifundazwe, nawesifundazwe. Ukuphila kwabantu kuthembele kukho.
UHailey Ockinga uyisishoshovu esiphikisana nokuvalelwa kwabantu ejele futhi ungumhleli womphakathi, futhi ungumqondisi ophethe weBeyond These Walls esifundazweni saseWashington.
U-Ethan Frenchman ungummeli weDisability Rights eWashington okhulumela abantu abakhubazekile emajele nasemajele.
Uthola kanjani ukuthi indiza yakho iBoeing 737 MAX
Kubagibeli abaningi, imodeli yendiza ayiyona into eyinhloko lapho kubhukwa indiza. Kodwa njengoba iningi lezindiza zeBoeing 737 MAX 9 limiswe ezweni lonke ngemva kokuphahlazeka kwesigubhu sezindiza i-Alaska Airlines ngoJanuwari 6, abanye abazoba abagibeli bangase bafune ukwazi ukuthi bangasho kanjani ukuthi bayohlala kuluphi uhlobo lwendiza nokuthi yiziphi izinhlobo eziphephe kakhulu. Eyokuqala kulula ukuyiphendula - eyesibili iyinkimbinkimbi ngokwengeziwe.
Ngokuvamile imodeli yendiza ibhalwa ohlwini lwemininingwane yokubhukha indiza. KuGoogle Flights, kufakwa emininingwaneni yendiza lapho uhlu lwandiswa, futhi ngokuvamile lubhalwa emakhasini okubhuka ezinkampani zezindiza ngazinye. Uma, ngasizathu simbe, uhlobo lwendiza lungabonakali kuGoogle Flights noma ekhasini lokubhukha, amasayithi afana ne-Expert Flyer neSeat Guru ahlanganisa imininingwane yendiza efana namamephu ezihlalo nohlobo lwendiza.
Ukunquma ukuthi iziphi izinhlobo zezindiza eziphephe kunazo zonke akulula kangako. INational Transportation Safety Board igcina imininingwane egcwele ephathelene nezingozi nezigameko. IFederal Aviation Administration iphinde inikeze imibiko yokuqala yezingozi nezigameko, okubandakanya nomkhiqizi wezindiza ezithintekayo, kusukela ezinsukwini ezingu-10 ezedlule ekhasini layo le-Aviation Safety Information Analysis and Sharing.
Enye imithombo ewusizo i-FAA exhumanisa nayo yiBoeing Worldwide Statistical Summary of Commercial Jet Airplane Accidents 1959-2022, ehlaziya ukuphepha kohlobo lwendiza ngokuhlukanisa izingozi ngokususelwa kumodeli yendiza. Ngokwalo mbiko, owawushicilelwa ngoSepthemba 2023, i-Boeing 787 ne-Airbus A350 yizona zinhlobo zezindiza ezinenani eliphansi kakhulu lokulahleka kwesikhumba, ingozi lapho indiza ibhujiswa khona ingalungiseki. Kunemodeli embalwa eyengeziwe kulo mbiko engakaze ihlupheke ngokulahlekelwa umkhumbi, kuhlanganise ne-Airbus A380 eyisikhulu esinezitezi ezimbili. Kodwa lezo zimodeli zaziqongelele ukuphuma okungaphansi kwesigidi esiyi-1 ngesikhathi sokubika.
Lo mbiko uphinde uhlanganise ukuqhathanisa kwezinga lezingozi zokulahleka kwesiqu ngesigidi sokuhamba, okusiza ukuchaza iqiniso lokuthi amanye amamodeli ajwayelekile noma abelokhu ekhona isikhathi eside kunamanye. I-Airbus A310, eyethulwa ngo-1983, inesilinganiso esiphakeme kakhulu sokulahlekelwa isiqu - 2.53 ngesigidi esiyi-1 sokuhamba - phakathi kwamamodeli asasebenza njengezindiza zabagibeli. Umkhaya we-Airbus 320, ohlanganisa i-A321 ne-A319neo, unesilinganiso esiphansi kunazo zonke, esingu-0,11. Indiza ye-Boeing 737 MAX, ibilokhu ikhona kusukela ngo-2017, unesilinganiso esingu-1.48.
Kubalulekile ukukhumbula ukuthi, nakuba la mazinga engamamitha ayisigidi, ezinye zezinhlobo zezindiza ezikule mbiko - ngokwesibonelo, iBoeing 727 eyethulwa ngo-1964 - bezilokhu zikhona amashumi eminyaka futhi ngenxa yalokho zazinesikhathi eside kakhulu sokuqongelela irekhodi lezingozi kunezinye.
UPerry Cooper, ummeleli wezindaba ePort of Seattle, eqondisa iSeattle-Tacoma International Airport, wathi ku-imeyili kunezizathu ezihlukahlukene zokuthi kungani izingozi zenzeka, kusukela esakhiweni kuya emaphutheni abantu. Ngakho nakuba kulula ukuthola ukuthi uzoba kuluphi uhlobo lwendiza, kunzima ngokwengeziwe ukuthola ukuthi lokho kusho ukuthini ngokombono wokuphepha.
Nakuba ungenza ukuqhathanisa okuthile kwamamodeli ezindiza okusekelwe emininingwaneni etholakalayo, i-FAA yeluleka ukuba ungazami ukuqhathanisa izindiza ngokusekelwe embikweni yazo yezingozi. Ngokombiko ocashunwe yilesi sikhulu, "okwamanje abukho ubufakazi obutholakala emininingwaneni yengozi obungasekela ukuhlelwa kwezindiza ngokwemibiko yazo yokuphepha."
Nakuba kuvame ukuba khona umehluko omkhulu phakathi kwamarekhodi ezokuphepha ezindiza nganoma yisiphi isikhathi, lokhu kubangelwa kakhulu "imvelo engavamile kodwa eyinhlekelele yengozi yezindiza," ngokusho kwe-FAA, futhi lo mehluko obonakalayo phakathi kwezindiza uyaphela ngokuhamba kwesikhathi. I-FAA yenqaba isicelo sokuphawula.
Indlela uBetta Edu aba ngayo isisulu sesimo sezombusazwe esikhohlakele
Esenzakalweni sakamuva esihilela uBetta Edu, uNgqongqoshe Wezindaba Zobuntu kanye Nokunciphisa Ubumpofu ekuphathweni kukaMengameli uBola Ahmed Tinubu, kube nezicelo zokususwa kwakhe esikhundleni phakathi kwezinsolo zokwebiwa kwemali eyizigidi ezingama-N585. UNgqongqoshe ubhekene nokugxekwa okukhulu komphakathi ngemva kokuvezwa kwememo lapho eyala u-Oluwatoyin Madein, uMcwaningimabhuku Jikelele (AG) wenhlangano, ukuba adlulisele izigidi ezingama-N585 kuyi-akhawunti yangasese.
Ngokwe-memorandamu eyavuza ngomhlaka-20 Disemba 2023, u-Edu wayala i-Accountant-General ukuthi idlulisele izimali ezivela ku-akhawunti yeNational Social Investment Office ku-akhawunti yangasese kaBridget Oniyelu, ongumcwaningi mabhuku wephrojekthi yokungenelela kobumpofu kaHulumeni waseFederal ebizwa ngokuthi "Izinsiza-mali Zamaqembu Abuthakathaka", iphrojekthi ngaphansi kukaNks. Inkonzo ka-Edu.
Ekhulumela u-Edu, uRasheed Zubair, umsizi wakhe kwabezindaba, uthi lesi senzo singokomthetho ngaphakathi kohlaka lomsebenzi kahulumeni waseNigeria. Kodwa-ke, kubalulekile ukuqaphela ukuthi lesi sicelo siphula izigaba ezahlukahlukene zeNigeria's Financial Regulations 2009, ezivimbela ngokusobala ukukhwabanisa nezinye izinhlobo zenkohlakalo ebhizinisini likahulumeni. Ngaphezu kwalokho, Isahluko Sesikhombisa, Isigaba 713 se-Financial Regulations 2009 yaseNigeria sisho ngokusobala ukuthi, "Imali yomuntu siqu ngeke ikhokhelwe kunoma yiziphi izimo kuyi-akhawunti yasebhange kahulumeni, futhi akukho mali yomphakathi okufanele ikhokhelwe kuyi-akhawunti yangasese". Iqhubeka ithi, "Noma isiphi isikhulu esikhokha imali yomphakathi siyiyise kuyi-akhawunti yangasese kubhekwa ngokungathi sikwenze ngenhloso yokukhwabanisa."
Engxoxweni neVentures Africa, iSikhulu Esiphezulu Sezomthetho, esingadalulwangwa ngegama sebhange eliholayo kwezentengiselwano saphawula, "Kunezinto eziningana eziphathelene nalolu daba. Okokuqala, umsebenzi wakhe musha, futhi owayengqongqoshe ngaphambi kwakhe nowayengumholi, uSadiya Umar-Farouk, wayehileleke emisebenzini eyayibonakala ingekho emthethweni. Kungase kube indlela abasebenza ngayo emsebenzini. Noma kunjalo, ukukhokhela imali yomphakathi kuma-akhawunti angasese kuphambene nemithetho yokuthengwa kwempahla yomphakathi". Wanezela ukuthi ngaphandle uma engakwazi ukunikeza isizathu esizwakalayo sokuvunyelwa okunjalo, kungase kungahileli inhloso yokukhwabanisa, kodwa nokho akulungile, futhi ukungaqiniseki.
Ngokwephosti yeTwitter, uchwepheshe wezokuxhumana kwezombusazwe kanye nezokuxhumana nge-digital u-Akin Akinwale uveze umbono wokuthi kungenzeka ukuthi umnyango awuzange ube nephutha ngokusebenzisa i-akhawunti yomuntu siqu.
Eveza imizwa efanayo ku-akhawunti yakhe yeTwitter, uMhlaziyi Wezombusazwe kanye noMeluleki Wezokuthuthukiswa Nokuphathwa, uBarrister Iyabo Awokoya, waveza ukuzwelana kwakhe noNgqongqoshe omisiwe. Wayekholelwa ukuthi kungenzeka ukuthi isikhonzi sasenze iphutha elingenacala ngenxa yokuzimisela ngentshiseko ukufeza umsebenzi waso.
Ngokusekelwe kulezi zimpikiswano zochwepheshe, kungacatshangwa ukuthi kunokungqubuzana emithethweni yezezimali phakathi kukahulumeni wesifundazwe nezinye izinhlangano zikahulumeni. Isimo saba sibi kakhulu lapho le dokhumenti evuzayo ivela obala, kwavela uBetta Edu njengembuzi yokuhlawulela uhlelo lwezepolitiki olungasebenzi kahle.
UCeleste uyintandokazi yami "umdlalo omncane omuhle we-freeware kuya emdlalweni omkhulu wezentengiselwano ogcwele ubuciko obunemininingwane yobuwula" arc yenkohlakalo ngoba ekuqaleni ukuthola i-dash ephindwe kabili kungamandla angenangqondo ebhokisini lomcebo futhi emdlalweni wezentengiselwano Kungenza Ngikhale
Ngokuvamile ngiyithanda kakhulu indlela le midlalo emibili esebenza ngayo. Inzuzo yezindaba ezimfushane iwukuthi "ungase weqe ungene engxenyeni enhle", zingaba ezihehayo futhi ezanelisayo ngokushesha. Inzuzo yezindaba ezinde ukuthi ungakwazi ukufaka noma yini eyenzekayo ngesisindo esingokomzwelo, ulahlekelwa ukushesha ngenxa yemivuzo enamandla.
Umdlalo wezohwebo iClimax of Celeste iwumdlalo we-pico-8 nje, okhulisiwe, ngamahora amaningana wokwakhiwa kwemishini nokulandisa okuyivumela ukuba iqhume kakhulu. ICeleste uyaziqhenya kakhulu ngomdlalo wayo omncane wabazali kangangokuthi ikhuluma ngezikhumbuzo, "i-2000 M... 2500 M... "ukuthuthuka, amandla-up, ifulege phezulu. Ikuvumela ukuba udlale umdlalo wokuqala kusukela esikrinini esiyinhloko!
UCeleste akayona "inguqulo enhle" noma "inguqulo eqediwe" yomdlalo we-pico-8, kumane nje kuyindlela ehlukile yendaba efanayo eyinhloko. Njengomuntu othanda kokubili ezimfushane nezide, ukubona ukuxhumana kuvezwe ngale ndlela kuyathakazelisa futhi kujabulisa ngempela.
Kukhona enye inguqulo esikalini esiphakathi eyayingase ibe khona phakathi kwalokhu okubili elandisa indaba efanayo eyandisiwe kodwa kwenziwe ngokokumiswa kwesikhathi esiqoqekile kanye nesikhathi esingasikhulu kakhulu sokukhiqiza. Ngicabanga ukuthi lokho bekuyoba ukuzalwa kabusha kwami, njengesimo sozwelo ... njengoba umdlali omkhulu womdlalo othengiswayo uyingxenye encane, ingedala intshisekelo enkulu enkundleni yokudlala emhlabeni ethandwa kakhulu kwezefiziksi yenkundla yokudlala, esawubunono uma ngicabanga.
Ngicabanga ukuthi kufanele ngithole umsebenzi, kodwa angive ngiyivila. Ngiqashe manje, ngizophuza wonke ubhiya wakho.
