I-anarchist ekhuluma kakhulu engafuni nokufihla ukuthi ingubani enikela nge-DNA yayo enkampanini ye-biotechnology ukuze ithole ikhophi engaqinisekile yo-"Mlando" wami. Yini engahamba kabi?
Umkami wayefuna ukuzenza njengesiqalo. Ngaphandle kokugxila kakhulu ezindabeni zakhe, unesizathu sokungabaza ukuthi abanye okhokho bakhe empeleni bangokhokho bakhe. Endabeni yami, ukuze ngimondle futhi ngibone umphumela wokuguquguquka kwezakhi zofuzo kusampula elincane, sinemibhalo ebanzi yomndeni.
Kungenzeka ngingumkhohlisi ongavamile emndenini wami, kodwa uma ngibheka izimpande zabantu abaningi emndenini wami abantulayo, noma yikuphi ukuziphathakabi kuvame emadolobhaneni amaningi ahlobene, amadolobhana amancane, nama-ghetto ezinhlanga lol.
Phela, uGogo wami washiya umyeni wakhe ngenxa kamfowabo, futhi nginomalume omkhulu ngakolunye uhlangothi owashiya umkakhe ngenxa kamalumekazi. Umkhaya wakithi ungase uzwane, kodwa ngeke uhlale isikhathi eside.
Futhi manje umkami unamahloni ngoba "Ukukhipha" kwami kwakushesha kakhulu kunalokho obekulindelekile. Ngiyaxolisa, mhlawumbe i-genome yakho akufanele yenze sengathi kunzima ukuyithola.
Imiphumela isifikile futhi, ngicela ungivumele, ivumelana ngokuphelele nomlando womkhaya wami. Ama-89.9% angamaBrithani nama-Irish iningi lawo ligxile emingceleni yaseScotland, entshonalanga ye-Ireland, eWales nase-cornwall. Akukhombisi kakhulu i-breton tho ngakho-ke noma zisondele kakhulu ku-cornish azibonakali zihlukile kimi noma umndeni wami wase-breton wawungekho ekuqaleni lapho .
Njengoba ngineminyaka engu-40 ubudala, bengikhathazeke ngokuthi ngangizothola ukuthi nginezingane engingazazi. Kuze kube manje, omunye womzala bami washiya izingane (mhlawumbe).
