Ngashiya i-FB, ngasusa yonke imishini yokulandelela iMeta nePinterest engosini yami futhi ngavala i-akhawunti yami yangasese yeWhatsApp.
Kanti ke izolo ngibuye ngasusa nesilandeli sangaphandle, i-Google Analytics, kuwebhusayithi yami futhi kuzwakala kumnandi lokho.
Ngisanda kubhalisela i-CRM esekelwe eYurophu ukuze ngithole ukwesekwa okungcono kwe-GDPR futhi ngithuthela ibhizinisi lami emasontweni ambalwa ezayo.
Ngidlulisele i-MX yami kuProton futhi manje ngine-SPF, i-DKIM ne-DMARC ephelele ngaphandle kokukhokhela iGoogle ngokuqinisekisa okuyisisekelo kwe-imeyili.
