#TeaganAir
Uma ungangibuza ukuthi ngikuchazele ukuthi kunjani ukushayela indiza encane, ngizothi inhlanganisa yesthuthuthu/ATV kanye neskebhe ngo-4000 ft emoyeni
Emhlabeni phansi izinto zenzeka ngokushesha. Kunentaba thizeni engazinzi phansi yingakho ngithi isthuthuthu/atv.
Futhi uma bewungazi, uqondisa indiza phansi ngemilenze yakho, hhayi ijoka yokulawula. Qondisa izinyathelo namabhuleki. Akuyona imoto.
Emoyeni kuyanyakazisa futhi kuyantanta kuzwakala ngathi usemkhunjini emanzini. Unokulawula, kodwa ngezinye izikhathi igagasi liyakushaya kancane, ngakho udinga imilenze yakho yolwandle ngaphandle kwasemoyeni.
Wo enye futhi indaba engahleliwe:
Ukundiza kungokomzimba. Namuhle *kubuhlungu* iqolo lami nemilenze ngathi ngiye ejimini.
Lokhu akufani nokungena nje emotweni ushayela ngeSonto uncebeleka. Kuyafana nezemidlalo kunokuthi uhambehambe olwandle ngokombono wami omusha.
UMgqibelo Omuhle zithandwa. Namukelekile ku-4000ft.
Ngiyabuyela kusasa futhi sizokwenza izitayela zokumisa nokushayela indiza kancane.
Usuku olubi namuhla, kodwa kumnandi kakhulu. Senze ukushayela indiza ngezinga eliphansi nezitayela zokumisa. Kwesinye isikhathi bekukhona lapho ijubane lethu lasemhlabeni beliphansi ku-16mph ngejubane lasemoyeni elingu 65.
Bekuwusuku oluhle olucacile, belulufifi kancane ekuphakameni, kodwa luluhle lunjanlo.
Ithreki yedatha ye-FlightAware.
#TeaganAir #pilot #flying #pa28 #PilotTraining
Lokhu kuyafana nokuya ejimini. Ngigcine sengilala amahora ama-2 (ngisanda kuvuka manje) ngoba umzimba ukhathele. Ngizwa nobuhlungu futhi, ikakhulukazi imilenze. Namuhla senza KAKHULU isiqondiso sakwesokudla sendiza.
Ngidinga isethi yokufaka emadlebeni.
