Ithuna Lesosha Elingaziwa isikhumbuzo sesosha elenze konke ukuze livikele izwe lalo. Leli Thuna Lesosha Elingaziwa elise-Arlington National Cemetery, e-Virginia, futhi eheha izigidi zezivakashi unyaka ngamunye, ivikelwe ngokuziqhenya abagadi bethuna. Amasosha e-3rd United States Infantry Regiment, i-Old Guard, athathe ilungelo lokugada Ithuna ngo-Ephreli ka-1948, futhi ayaqhubeka nokufeza lo msebenzi ongcwele. Ithuna Lesosha Elingaziwa ligadwe amahora angama-24 ngosuku, izinsuku eziyisithupha ngeviki, nezinsuku ezingama-365 ngonyaka, iminyaka engama-77 edlule.
