Ngemva kokushintshela kuyiyunifomu encane, ngasiza isikhashana, kwakulula ngaphandle kokufletha nokushelwa isikhathi esiningi abantu; kodwa akuzange kungikhathaze uma ngikhuluma iqiniso. Ngizokhuluma no-Anton ngemva kweshifu, kusadingeka ngiyeke ukucabanga ngo-Al, ngisho noma ngazi ukuthi ngisazo kwenza uphenyo la ahlala khona ngemva kwalapha, kodwa nje…
Kwaphuma amalangabi emlonyeni kaThassalin njengoba iThraki enamandla ithungela umlilo ehlathini elithile, wabe esesekeleza phezulu, wabuka isikhashana. Ngokungavamile, njengoba ehlisa ijubane, umsindo wokuklabalasa ovele emva kwakhe wathula. UThassalin wayesekhohliwe ukuthi unabagibeli ngemuva.
Kahle Tenuk, uke washintsha waba iThraki ngaphambili!
Ibhanoyi lami lihluke kakhulu ekuhudulweni ngokushesha idragoni enkulu ephinki!
Akukubi kangako, angithi, Kayel?
Kuyacaca ukuthi uKayel akavumelani noNyssi, ubekeke emnyama kancane kunokuvamile futhi izinzipho zakhe bezigubhe umhlane kaThassalin kangangokuthi wenza iThraki yopha, kodwa kusobala ukuthi uThassalin ebengenandaba. Ngalokho okushiwo, uThassalin wabona ukuthi ulimaze abangane bakhe abasha wabe esefuna indawo angehlela kuyo.
"UNGIXOLELE NGIZWE IPHUNGA. BEKUMELWE NGIBHEKANE NALO!"
Besikhona isidingo sokuthi usihudule nathi? UTenuk ushibilikile njengoba ehla emhlane kaThassalin, eshushuluzela emsileni wakhe. "Futhi sishiye uRetvik emuva! Silahle indoda yethu yempi enkulu, nenamandla! Uzosithola kanjani?"
Uzobona naye... esho ngezwi eliphezulu uNyssi. "URetvik uthatha kade kodwa akasona isiphukuphuku."
Yah kodwa uyakwazi yini ukushayela uRetvik?
UNyssi wacifa iso wabe esebuyela emuva kuTenuk. "Yebo uyakwazi ukushayela."
Wake wambona uRetvik eshayela imoto? Akanalo iloli njengawe futhi angikaze ngimbone eshayela into efana nemoto encane enhle njengeyaKayel, uqale ukuya emsebenzini ngemoto ngoba wena ulokhu usihambisa emsebenzini. Una lesiya sithuthuthu sakhe.
Ukuqhuma kohleko kwabaphazamisa. UThassalin wachazeka ngokushesha, kodwa akekho otholile ukuthi ubehlekani. Kuthathe isikhathi eside ukuba uThassalin ehlise umoya.
NINGIXOLELE, KODWA NGIVELE NGABONA UMNGANE WAKHO OMKHULU, ESITHUTHUTHWINI ESINCANE ESENZELWE BONA KUNEZINGANE. KUYAHLEKISA! NGIFISA NGABE BENIKWAZI UKUBONA. UMBONO OYIGUGU! ENGINGEKE NGIKWAZI UKUNIBONISA WONA!
UKayel wagigitheka, njengoba ecabanga lokhu obekucatshangea uThassalin. "Yah, unephuzu. Kodwa yini oyitholile futhi kungani undize ngokushesha kangaka?"
UThassalin wenza umsindo wengulube, wabe esephuma wanyamalala isikhashana, ngaphambi kokuba abuye, uwise isilwane esifile phambi kukaNyssi. Kwakuyi-Orothrack, isilwane esithi asibe yidragoni elingavamile, elinombala wegolide nomhlophe. Kodwa sasingenakhanda. "ESINYE ESIFILE. NGEZWA UKUKHALA. NGANUKA IGAZI LAZO. NGIDONSELEKA EKUVIKELENI NASEKUZINGELENI. NJENGOBA KUFUNWA IYISINI. IZILWANE, ZISEDUZE."
IThraki enkulu yavele yama. UNyssi kanye noKayel nabo bama, bavele banaka isikhala. Kunento enkulu emnyama ebagqolozele, yenza umsindo ka-s. Noma yini obekuyiyo, kuvule amaphaphu amabili kwabe sekuhamba, iqonde kuThassalin, akunandaba nokuthi kufanele kudlule izilwane ezintathu ezincane. UKayel noTenuk kukwaze ukumboza kuphela, kodwa uNyssi uzithole ehuduleka futhi ucishe wawela kuThassalin.
UThassalin uphendule kulokhu kuhlaselwa ngokubambelela ku-Nyssi nokumlahla ngomhlane ngomsila wakhe omude ngokubabazekayo, ngaphambi kokundizela emoyeni. Isilwane esimnyama namaphiko amabili ngokushesha sibagijimisile.
UKayel wenza umsindo wokucasuka njengoba edonsa isibhamu emva kwakhe, wabe esevula isikhama, kwavela ibhande lakhe lezinhlamvu. Ulengise ibhande lakhe esifubeni sakhe ukuze kube lula ukulisebenzisa, kodwa ngokushesha waqaphela ukuthi uNyssi, iThraki nesilo kunyamalele.
WeTenuk, ungakwazi ukushintshela kokuthile okungandiza? kubuza uKayel.
"Ufuna ukubajaha?"
Yebo, kucacile.
Kodwa... oyedwa wabo uyisilo esikhulu!
Ngakho? Nginesibhamu esinamandla ezandleni zami, njengamanje, sivivile. Ngidinga nje ukukwazi, uyazi, ukusibona, ukuze ngizosidubula.
UTenuk wanqikaza, wabe esehlehlela emuva, enginikeza isikhala. Ngokugqumela phansi kobuhlungu, umzimba kaTenuk waluleka, uboya bakhe baba njengama-scales futhi izingalo zakhe zaba izimpiko. Washintsha ngokushesha waba iThraki, eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka evamile kodwa amehlo akhe ahlala ebomvu.
"Gibela"
Njengoba ese yiThraki evamile, uTenuk manje sebenamapuleti ama-scales emhlane wakhe, kodwa uzokwazi futhi nokumila izimpondo emhlane ukuze uKayel ezokwazi ukubambelela kuzo. Kuthathe isikhathi eside ukuba uTenuk abe nezimpiko, kodwa uma eke waba semoyeni, ngokushesha ukuzimama wabe esezama ukubajaha.
Nokho, uTenuk noKayel ngokushesha babonile ukuthi ababodwa. Isilwane sesibili esimnyama siqhamuke ngaphansi kwabo, futhi uTenuk ukwaze kuphela ukuvimbela ukushayiseka.
Ngicabanga ukuthi lokho kungezinye zesilo esikhulu nesisabekayo uLanex abekhathazeke ngaso? UKayel uveze izinhlonzo njengoba ezama ukudubula isilo okwesibili, ugejile wabe esesihlohla ngokushesha.
UTenuk akazange aphendule, ebematasa ezama ukugxila kuNyssi noThassalin, ngisho noma esinye isilo besibajaha. UKayel ngokungavamile wajika, ukuze abhekane nesilo. Ukuthi bekubajaha bekuyizindaba ezinhle emehlweni kaKayel, kwenze kwalula ngami ukucibishela umlilo. Imicibisholo idlule izimpika zesilo, futhi imemeze ngobuhlungu, sanyamalala ngaphansi kwezihlahla. Lapho sisabalandela, uKayel wayangaqiniseki, kodwa ibingeke ikwazi ukubajaha.
Phambili, uNyssi wayebambelele njengoba uThassalin ekhipha umlilo eshisa isilo ngamalangabi omlilo. Ngesikhathi isilwane silimala, sibukeke sinolaka ngempela futhi singakulungele ukubuyela emuva, amabhola omlilo akubukeki ngathi ayakwenza lokho okufanele akwenze. Njengoba uThassalin ezilula, uNyssi uthatha njengethuba lokukhipha isikhali, isibhamu esikade sikhona. Yiqiniso ukuthi asenzelwanga lokhu kodwa esidubula konke besizoba ngcobo esilweni esimnyama?
Cha, kuyacaca akunjalo. Isilwane sivele sabhonga sabe sesindiza saqonda kuThassalin. Ngenhlanhla, nakuba emkhulu, uThassalin yanyakaza ngokushesha ngokwanele ukusuka endleleni, kodwa uNyssi akakwazanga ukuzibamba wamemeza njengoba ecishe washibilika emhlane osheleleyo kaThassalin.
SIZIBULALA KANJANI? kumemeza uNyssi.
DUBULA AMAKHANDA!
KUZOBA NZIMA LOKHO!
UThassalin wabhonga, wabe esezungeza, eduze kwentaba ayibiza ngekhaya. Isilo esimnyama salandela, kodwa wathuka njengoba ilangabi lomlilo lishaya ngemva. Isilwane sibonile ukuthi asisodwa. Sithuke nakakhulu njengoba uThassalin ehlisa ijubane wabe eseshaya umsila wakhe eceleni kwekhanda lesilo, esiwisa phansi.
Sibhonga futhi senza umsindo wenyoka, isilwane sindizele phezulu, sikhafula emoyeni. Ngokuzumayo konke kuvele kwamnyama, njengokungathi isilo sivele saqeda konke ukukhanya esibhakabhakeni, kwasala ifu lobusuku obungapheli.
Asisakwazi ukusibona, uThassalin uzamile ukuhlehla kodwa wazithola esethinta isiqongo sesihlahla ngaphambi kokuwela endaweni esobala. Isilo besazi ngqo ukuthi uThassalin uwele kuphi futhi saya kuye, sashona phansi nefu elimnyama.
Kayel! UTenuk wamemeza njengoba ehla efwini futhi ezungeza, ezama ukubheka uNyssi neThassalin ngaphansi eibumnyameni. "Senzenjani? Kayel..? Kayel, ukuphi?"
Ngezansi, uNyssi uphuphutha ezinyaweni zakhe. Wayeqiniseka ngokuthi uphule okuthile, kodwa amandla akhe angavamile, abeseqalile ukusebenza. Angeke sisho okufanayo ngoThassalin, obelele egqumeni, encike esihlahleni esingawanga ngenxa yesisindo sakhe. UNyssi wenze okusemandleni akhe ukuze azame ukufinyelela uThassalin kodwa ebengakwazi ukubona amamitha ambalwa phambi kwakhe. Yonke into ibimnyama futhi igcwele izithunzi. Futhi esithunzini, kunento eklabalasa futhi imemeza.
Umsila omubi, ohlangahlangene ophansi eduze noNyssi, umqumba phansi. Uphawule ukuthi umsila ubunyakaza nje ungaqondile kuye. Isilwane, okuncane akubonile nakuzwile uNyssi, imisindo eyenziwa izithunzi. Kunento ehamba ebumnyameni, ugwaza isilo, isidida ingqondo.
Ngokushesha kwezwakala umsindo wesibhamu, futhi isilo siwe buthule, saquleka phansi futhi sahlala kanjalo. Ubumnyama obubazungezile banyamalala, kwavela obekwenzekile. Ume phezu kwesilwane uKayel, ubambe isibhamu nokuphefumelela phezulu.
Lokho ku... ngolunye loshintsho olungavamile engake ngalwenza... Thanto kat'olon... uKayel wadonsa umoya. Amehlo akhe ngandlela thile ebekhazimula ubumnyama, futhi amandla amnyama adlulele emzimbeni wakhe. Nokho, njengoba ekhuluma, umbala wabuyela kokuvamile kukaKayel futhi amehlo akhe abuyeka embaleni ophuzi ngokuvamile.
Kumthathe isikhathi uNyssi ukuqonda ukuthi kwenzekeni. Bonke baqaphelile ukuthi uKayel unamandla okuguquka angavamile, angajwayele ukuwasebenzisa ngoba iningi labo liwabheka njengangengcwele noma asabisayo. Kodwa uNyssi ubengazi ukuthi uKayel angasebenzisa lawo mandla kunoma yibuphi ubumnyama. Okunye ukuthi uKayel ube zenzisa, ebemangele ngempela.
Ukahle? UNyssi akakwazanga ukuzibamba wavele wabuza.
Yah, ngikahle. Kunento engiyibulalile, ngizoba kahle kungekudala. UKayel wahlola lokho akwenzile, njengoba uTenuk ehlile futhi wama eduze kwakhe, uguquke waba sesimweni sakhe esivamile se-Spast.
Manje njengoba isilwane sasesinganyakazi, sebengabona kangcono ukuthi siyini. Isikhumba saso simnyama futhi sinoketshezi, kodwa uketshezi lwaluvaleleke emzimbeni wesilwane. Sinezimpiko ezine nezinyawo ezine, konke bekunezinzipho ezinde, futhi sinezimpondo ezimbili eziqondile eziphuma ekhanda.
Ngaphambi kukaTenuk noKayel ungababuza ukuthi bebebukani, kunento ememezayo futhi yaphuma ehlathini. Nokho, ayizange ihlangane namuntu, njengoba imoto evamile iyishayise eceleni kwayo yawa ezinyaweni zikaNyssi. Ngokungananazi, uNyssi wakhipha isibhamu ngokushesha wabe esidubula enhloko, ebulala isilwane ngokushesha.
Oops... URetvik wahleba esesihlalweni somshayeli, ngaphambi kokucisha injini wabe esehle elolini. "Eh, bengingaqondile ukukwenza lokho. Ingabe nonke nikahle?"
Uphuthelwe yikho konke okwenzekile! kumemeza uTenuk. "Ubukuphi?"
Nonke ningishiyile ngandlela thile. Ngifike la ngokushesha okukhulu... kusho uRetvik. "Ngingabuza, ziyini leziya zinto ezimbi?"
Umbuzo kaRetvik ngenhlanhla uphendulwe uThassalin, ovukile. Ebegcwele ukusikeka nemihuzuko futhi ebonakala ehanjelwe ingqondo kancane, kodwa akabukeki elimele kakhulu.
UBULALE I-CORRUPTIIDS! IZILO EZITHELELEKILE. IZILO ZAHAMBA LAPHA NGESIKHATHI INKOHLAKALO IHLASELE ONKULUNKULU BAKHO.
Usho... lento embi unkulu yesilo le... esizame ukuyibulala? kwasho uTenuk.
YEBO. YONA LEYO. KUNGENZEKA UKUTHI ZININGI. KODWA ANGIKWAZANGA UKUZIDUBULA EKHANDA. BENGINGENASO ISIBHAMU. FUTHI OKUBILI KOKUKODWA AKUNABULUNGISA, YEBO? UThassalin wasondela eduze kwaKayel wabe esembambatha ekhanda. "SIYABONGA, MNCANYANA. UNGIKHUMBUZA UMNGANI WAMI WAKUDALA U-ARKADIN. LINDELA ABABULALI ABAMBALWA NABANGAKWAZI UKUBULALA."
Uh... ngiyabonga... ngicabanga... Kayel esho ngokungabaza. "Ngakho, uh, siqedile la?"
Kusho uNyssi ngokungabaza, wabe esethatha ikhamera, wathatha izithombe ezithile zezilwane ezifile. Wabe esehosha umkhonto wakhe awuthandayo, obukhali, nobizayo, futhi waqala ukusika izimpondo zesilwane, ngaphambi kokudlulela kwezinye. Nokho, njengoba uNyssi eqeda, izilwane zivele zasha, futhi ngokushesha zaba umlotha. Kwenzeke into efanayo ngezimpondo ezisikwe uNyssi.
Eh... lokho kuhle futhi kubi... kusho uNyssi. "Ngicabanga ukuthi okungenani nginezithombe?"
Isandulela
“Ngiyacela!” Kuncenga indlovukazi u-Eirwen, “ungamxoshi! Ungumntwana nje!” Inkosi Yeqhwa yabuka phansi kumkayo ehleli esihlalwenis sobukhosi, umeluleki wayo wasebukhosini eseduze kwayo. Waye zele intombazane. Wacasulwa yilowo mbono.
Intombazane ibukeka kakhulu njengonina wayo; amehlo aluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka nezinwele ezimhlophe ezihlobiswe ngemidweshu eluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka. Inkosi Yeqhwa icabange ukuthi indodakazi imenza abukeke buthaka. Phela, ibilokhu ithola amadodana kwaze kwaba yillesi sikhathi.
“Ukuphela kwezinto ongakhetha kuzo ukubulala umntwana noma ukumlahla ehlane. Lesi isijeziso sesenzo sakho esingalungile, Eirwen.” Waphimisela igama lakhe ngazathi ushevu. Uhlale enza kanjalo.
IFrostfell kwakungewona umbuso owodwa. Wawuhlukene phakathi, iNyakatho kanye neNingizimu. ENyakatho, umbuso ongenamilingo. ENingizimu, umbuso ogcwele ukubonakaliswa kwamandla wemibono. Ngenxa yokuhaha, imibuso emibili yashayisana empini engapheli, kwaze kwaba yilapho iNingizimu yacela umaluju.
INingizimu ngokuphelelwa yithemba, nomndeni wasebukhosini ungenza noma yini ukuze uvimbele uchitheka kwegazi. Banikeza ngokuphela kwenkosazane yabo ukuba ibe indlovukazi yaseNyakatho futhi izale indodana ezoba inkosi yesikhathi esizayo. Ngemva kwalokho, iNingizimu ibihlangana neNyakatho ukuze kube umbuso owodwa. INyakatho yavuma, futhi Inkosazana u-Eirwen yashada iNkosana u-Akull.
“Ngiyakunxusa, nkosi yami, esikhundleni sengane yami ukuze iphephe, yenza noma yini ngami, ngivalele, ngixoshe, noma ngisho ungibulale.” kuncenga Indlovukazi u-Eirwen, ephethe umntwana wakhe ezingalweni zakhe.
Inkosi Yeqhwa yabheka phansi endlovukazini yayo, ngokwenyaya emehlweni ayo. Mhlawumbe, mhlawumbe, ingase ibe nobubele. Owesifazane ahlale naye iminyaka engamashumi amabili nambili, ohlale eyikhathalela ngezikhathi ezizwa ephansi, omzalele amadodana ayo.
“Kulungile. Umntwana angahlala esigodlweni.” Yaqala, ukububula kwendlovukazi. “Kodwa,” inezela. “Uzobulawa.”
Bobabili umeluleki neNdlovukazi u-Eirwen babonisa ubuso obuthukile. Yabuka phansi. “Yebo, nkosi yami.” Wakhothama.
Inkosi Yeqhwa yayala umeluleki wasebukhosini ukuba ithathe indodakazi yendlovukazi kwamanye amagumbi ka-Eirwen angenamuntu. Lapho lokho sekwenziwe wayala ukuba onogada ukuba balethe u-Eirwen endaweni yokubulala, lapho bonke abantu bendawo bezobona khona.
Njengoba onogada beyihambisa endaweni, abantu bendawo bakhala kalusizi lapho bebona ukuphela kwendlovukazi yabo- nenomusa- izobulawa. Abanye abantu bakhala, abanye bebememeza futhi bezama ukuhlasela onogada, futhi abanye bebezibuza ukuthi kungani lokhu kwenzeka; kodwa bonke bebenombono ofanayo.
“Mkhululeni!”
“Kungani benza lokhu kuye?”
Njengoba u-Eirwen esondela esigxotsheni sokhuni, kwavela umuntu osatshwayo embusweni. Umsebenzisi womlilo. Obeyindlovukazi u-Eirwen wayezoshiswa aze afe. Akekho umuntu ofanelekelwe ukufa, ngisho nezigebengu. Kwakuyinto enesihluku ongayenza kumuntu eFrostfell.
U-Eirwen wayeboshiwe esigxotsheni inkosi yabe isiqala ukukhuluma ngendlela indlovukazi ebakhaphele ngayo. Abantu baseFrostfell benqaba ukukholelwa futhi abawamukelanga amazwi akhe. Ngemva kwalokho, umsebenzini womlilo wabasa isigxobo umlilo, futhi unyembezi lwehla ebusweni bendlovukazi.
“Mana njalo, Kari.” Lokho kwaba ukuphela kokubusa kweNdlovukazi u-Eirwen.
Kwathuleka Emahholo
Phaca, phaca, phaca yilokho kuphela ongakuzwa egumbini eliqhelile ngakwesobunxele eningizimu esigodlweni esibandayo. Izinceku ezidlulayo zazihlezi zizibuza ukuthi yini esegumbini, zesaba okwakuphakathi. Amahemuhemu ayehamba emaphaseji phakathi kwezisebenzi. Kwakucatshangwa ukuthi inkosikazi yeNkosi Yeqhwa u-Eirwen, yayikuleliya gumbi, ilinde ukukhululwa.
Bebenganembile. kucabanga u-Ivory, njengoba eya ohlangothini lwaseningizimu, njengoba izisebenzi ezidlula emaphaseji zihlebelana. Abazi nhlobo ukuthi kunani lapha.
Amahemuhemu, yiqiniso, ayemthinta naye njengoba kwakunguye kuphela owayevunyelwe ukungena egumbini.
Qo qo. “Ntokazi uKari, ingabe ukhona?” kuhleba u-Ivory emnyangweni oyinkimbinkimbi, eyayineqhwa kanye nomqhele, uphawu lomndeni wasebukhosini.
Bazibuza ukuthi uzobavumela yini ukuba bangene, ngokungafani ngezikhathi ezedlule bahamba bayobuza. Ngisanesibazi sangesikhathi esedlule. U-Ivory wahleka lapho ekhumbula lokho. UKari ulahle incwadi emahlombe abo, kodwa lapho ebona ukubani, waxolisa ngokushesha.
Isigi esisodwa sivele phakathi, kubukeka ngathi ebephakathi, phela ayikho enye indawo abaya kuyo.
“Ngingangena?” kubuza u-Ivory, ukukhumbula isikhathi abangena ngaso bengacelanga.
Isigi esisodwa sezwakala ngaphakathi. Yebo, kuyafaneleka ukuthi. U-Ivory kuqhaqhazela, ngenxa yamakhaza kanye nomsindo. Kuyinto engavamile ngo-Ivory ukuzwa umsindo ovela egumbini okucatshangwa ukuthi alinamuntu, ngisho noma bebengena kulona iminyaka eminingi.
“Ngiyangena.” Kusho u-Ivory, evula umnyango kancane. Akubona egumbini kwakungavamile, ngokwezindinganiso zabantu abavamile, kodwa akuyona into engalindelekile. Amaphepha ebegcwele yonke indawo. Izincwadi bezisakazeke yonke indawo, itafula eliphukile, futhi kugcwele amaqhwa abaziwe. Awekho amawindi futhi ukukhanya kufana nokuthi akukho. Futhi bekubanda ukwedlula yonke indawo esigodlweni (okwakusho lukhulu). Igumbi libukeke njengesiphepho seqhwa esishaya indawo.
Intombazane egumbini yayihleli embhedeni, izigoqe ngengubo njengoba ifunda enye yezincwadi zayo. Kunesibani esincane esikhanyisa indawo.
“Iyiphi incwadi leyo?” kubuza u-Ivory, uhlala phansi eduze kuka- Kari embhedeni wakhe.
Uvule ikhasi elingenalutho wabe esebhala usuku kulo. Ngaphansi kwalo, wabhala, “5/11/648 -12/13/648.”
“Embula izinkumbulo zakudala?” Kubuza u-Ivory, ebuka incwadi endala. UKari wanqekuzisa ikhanda. “Ucabanga ukuthi bazokukhulula ngoKhisimusi? Usezinsukwini ezimbalwa nje.”
UKari ushaye kabili isibani. Cha, njengoba ebecabanga ngo- Ivory. Inkosi Yeqhwa ayikaze imkhiphele ngaphandle uKari, njengoba wayebhekwa “njengephutha” emehlweni ayo. Wazalwa ethule futhi uwukuphela kwentombazane emndenini wakhe, njengoba kwakugcwele abafana.
Kungokufanayo ngo-Ivory, ngendlela yabo ekhethekile. Lapho u-Ivory evela obala njengonobulili obubili, kubonakala ngazathi izwe lashintsha nalo. Banikezwa imisebenzi ezokwenza ukuba bachithe isikhathi bodwa isikhathi esiningi, njengesijeziso soba abahlukile.
Baphoqwa ukuba basebenze njengencekukazi yenkosazana. Bebengena nkinga kangako, njengoba bengabangane futhi.
“Maduze kuzoba usuku lwakho lokuzalwa, angithi?” Kubuza u-Ivory, ekhumbula ukuthi usuku lokuzalwa lwenkosazana luzoba ezinsukwini ezimbalwa. Wanqekuzisa ikhanga uKari, ngamehlo aluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka adabukisayo.
“Uyafuna ukulugubha?” Babuza, bebhekisela ngesikhathi ephendula ngokudlule.
Cha. UKari waphuma. U-Ivory wayazi ukuthi ingxoxo enzima le kuye. Kwakuwusuku avalelwa ngalo egumbini lakhe futhi umama wakhe waxoshwa. U-Ivory wayesangumntwana nje lapho kwenzeka, kodwa bakhumbula indela abantu bendawo nezinceku ababecasuke ngayo. Babezwile ukuthi Indlovukazi u-Eirwen yayiyindlovukazi enomusa, kodwa futhi wayebikezela izinto ezazizokwenzeka.
“Ngakho… yini enifuna ukuyenza?” Babuza. UKari wababuka, egcwele injabulo. Unike u-Ivory iphepha. Lapho belibuka nokho…
