“Ufuna ngikutholele lezi zinto?” U-Ivory waphendukela kuyinkosazane, owayethepha kakhulu, imisila yengulube ngapha nangapha. “Yebo?” Bagigitheka kancane njengoba bebona inkosazane ngokuvamile enamahloni ibonisa ukuthanda into ethile. Kwakuqala ukuba icele into engahlobene nezincwadi ezazingekho egumbini layo.
“Okay! Ngizobuye nginibone" u-Ivory, wasukuma enza indlela emaphepheni amaningi nezincwadi.
UKari wavuma ngekhanda, ebuyela emuva ezinkumbulweni zakhe futhi ezigoqa ngengubo yakhe ewugqinsi.
Baphuma egumbini, bekhululekile ngokuthi inkosazana ekugcineni izama ezinye izinto futhi icela izinto ngaphandle kwamandla ayo, njengopende.
Bahamba emahholo futhi, bazama ukugwema amahemuhemu ezisebenzi futhi.
“Ngizwe ukuthi ungenwe umoya weNdlovukazi u-Eirwen, yingakho ehlala eya kuleliya gumbi.”
“Ngizwa kuthiwa udla ingane kuleliya gumbi.”
“Ubukeka njengendoda, akukubi yini lokho?”
Bavala izindlebe zabo, njengoba ukuviba kungasebenzi. Baya egumbini lasebukhosini lompeni, elalisengxenyeni esempumalanga, umnyango wesibili wesobunxele.
U-Ivory wafika emnyango oyinkimbinkimbi njengowaKari. Kuwona kwakuneDragoni Elimhlophe, elinye lamadragoni angu-6 okuqala, asungula iFrostfell. Kwenza ingqondo ukuthi umpendi abe nalokho emnyango, uthanda umlando.
Bavula umnyango, belindele ukubona okuvamile. Uphende ugcwele yonke indawo, amapensela namaphepha asabalele egumbini, amashidi okuphenda agcwele izindonga. Ngokungalindelekile, bathola enye indawo. Yayihlanzekile, futhi lapho ngemuva kwakunombala obomvu oyivelvet kanye nesistulo phambi kwayo. Esitulweni kwakunoMqhele weNkosana u-Aquilo, kupendwa isithombe sakhe.
“Ah, sawubona, Ivory! Uyafuna ukubona inkosi yesikhathi esizayo yenza isithombe sayo?” Kubuza u-Aquilo, ecifela u-Ivory iso.
“Uxolo, nkosana,” Basho, bebe bemziba kancane futhi bebheka izinto ezifunwa umngani wabo othulayo. “Ngimane ngila ukuze ngizothatha izinto zokupenda.”
“Aw mantombazane nizosheshe nihambe? Kubuza u-Aquilo, “Kodwa bengifuna ukunibona!”
“Mina angifuni.” U-Ivory athole izinto zokupenda ohlwini lwabo azifake enqoleni abayitholile. “Futhi angiyona intombazane.”
Inkosana ayikucabanganga lokho. “Aw muntuza, uyazi ngimane ngiyasho nje! Uzobona kuzokuphuma uma usumdala!” Washo, amagama okudelela.
“Kumelwe ngihambe.” Kusho bona, ngokushesha bazizwa bengakhululekile ngesikhathi kuphendula inkosana. Bekhumbula zonke izinto ezimbi abantu abazisho kuye mayelana nobulili babo. Ngifuna ngempela ukusuka eduze kwakhe.
“Seniyahamba njalo?” Inkosana ngokushesha yavela emnyango, eziba ukukhononda komapendana oyedwa wasebukhosini.
“Lena akuyona indlela inkosi yesikhathi esizayo okufanele iziphathe ngayo!” Basho ngolaka.
“Akekho ozokwazi. Abantu ngeke bakukholwe futhi umpendi ngeke asho lutho uma efuna ukuphila.” Wabuka umpendi isikhashana, wabe esencika ku-Ivory. “Nithini ngokuthi nginikhiphe?” Baqhaqhazela. Kulungile, bazwile izinsongo izikhathi eziningi ezedlule, kodwa bekungezona ezenkosana, ezoba yinkosi.
“Uyazi ukuthi igama elithi ‘cha’ lisho ukuthini?” Bathimisa, baphusha umqhele wenkosana kude nabo.
“Chabo.” Kuphendula u-Aquilo, emamatheka. Yiqiniso inkosana ithola yonke into eyifunayo ayazi ukuthi igama lisho ukuthini.
U-Ivory wagoqa amehlo akhe. “Kungani ufuna ukungikhipha kubo bonke abantu? Unabantu, angazi, abakufanele abangu-100?”
Wangenela, esamomotheka, “empeleni bangu-500.” Wathinta izinwele zakhe emuva, eziphebeza emoyeni obandayo.
“Yabona! Kungani ukhetha mina kubo bonke abantu? Ngiyinkinga.” Bazanga ngezingalo zabo.
“Uyintombazane enhle kunawo wonke engike ngawabona.” U-Aquilo wambamba ngaphansi kwesilevu sakhe ngesithupha sakhe esisodwa futhi u-Ivory waphoqeleka ukuba abheke phezulu ambuke.
Isahluko 1
Cohren
0430 isikhathi sase-Itania. UCohren wayekuzonda ukuvuka ekuseni kanje. Ngokuyinhloko ngoba kwakuwomthwalo wakhe ukuvusa wonke umuntu ekhampanini yakhe. Uphuma buthule embhedeni wakhe, wangena esimweni sokulwa, elahla isivikelo sakhe sesifuba, wabe esepakisha izinto zakhe ezikuyi-locker, ecophelela ngebhokisi elithile. Wabamba isibhamu sakhe wabe esefaka isigqoko esibambweni esincane esihlobene nebhande lakhe. Besinakokho konke ukulungisa, okokuphefumula, izibuko, yonke into edingekayo. Ngemva kokubheka izinhlamvu zakhe, buthule waphuma emkhomeni, udaka neqhwa kunamathele ngaphansi kwamabhuthi akhe.
Wakhipha umentshisi kuyijakhethi yakhe kanye nogwayi kwelinye iphakethe. Njengoba ekulayitha, wathi ukudonsa kancane ngaphambi kokuvula umnyango. Ngaphezu kweviki eledlule kuye kwadingeka ukuba ahlakaniphe ukuze avuse amadoda kanye nabesifazane. Wayeka ukusebeenzisa i-alamu yamanje, isikhathi esiningi akuzange kusebenze, lapho konke lokhu kuvela ezipikheni kwenza umsindo ka-s omncane.
“Ebavusa” UCohren waphenduka ukuze abuke uLieutenant wesibili uNemic ehamba.
“Yebo” kuphendula uCohren.
“Uhlele ukusebenzisa ini namhlanje?”
Ngaphambi kokuba aphendule, kwavuleka umnyango futhi uHarris, uCraith, nabanye abambalwa basheshe baphuma, sebegqokile kakade futhi belungele usuku.
“Sawubona,” kusho uCraith.
“Nivuswe yini madoda?” kubuza uCohren.
“Okokuqala, besingafuni ukubona ukuthi yini obunayo engqondweni ukuze uvuse abantu namhlanje. Okwesibili, iShock Troops yokuqala ezovuka izothola ukudla kokuqala kwasekuseni” Omunye wamadoda, uRavik, waphendula. “Futhi uyazi empeleni ukuthi kungaba kubi kanjani”
“Wenza iphuzu elihle Specialist,” kusho uCohren. Wafinyelela wabe esekhuphula iswichi. Kwakhala i-alamu phakathi endaweni yokulala, umsindo omkhulu ngohlabayo. Wezwa ukuxokozela kwabantu phakathi nabantu begxobana.
“Jeez Valturi,” kusho uNemic. “Ubungacabanga ukuthi ngalesi sikhathi sebefundile ukuvuka ngesikhathi uvuka”
“Abangane bami bakuyi-boot camp lapha bakwenzile” UCohren waya kuHarris, uCraith nakuRavik. “Kodwa futhi, iqembu labo nomholi weplatoon, bayazi ukuthi kumelwe bavuke ngaphambi kwezisebenzi.
Emizuzwini ekamuva bonke abasele babantu baphume bememeza. Bonke bebe nakho konke abakudingayo, kusukela ezintweni zabo zomuntu siqu kuye kumagiya adingekayo. Abambalwa kwabaqeqeshwayo abasha babukeka behlangahlangene, abanye bacikekile.
“Sanibonani nonke” UCohren washo ngezwi elijabulile.
“Ngayo yonke inhlonipho, kungani kufanele usivuse sonke kanjalo?” Kubuza omunye wabaShock Troopers, iphoyisa.
“Ngoba ama-alamu avamile ayabheda. Nanokuthi iDaybreak ayilali” kusho uCohren.
“Qiniseka ukuthi unazo zonke izinto zakho,” kusho uCohren. Njenge-Lieutenant yokuqala kanye neKhampani XO, bekuwumthwalo wakhe ukubheka nokusiza abantu kanye nomholi weKhampani, uKaputeni uBoradin Shaw . “Ngeke sibuye. Amasegenti kanye nama-lieutenants esibili, nginikeza wena neqembu lakho imizuzu eyishumi nanhlanu ukuba nenze ukuhlola kokugcina futhi nibambe okosuku”
Amalungu ekhampani ye-Exodus ngokushesha aphuma. Babe yingxenye ye-2nd Shocktrooper Division, ne-2nd Army. Ekuqaleni kwakungamakhampani amabili ahlukene, iCohort ne Dagger, ngaphambi kokuba kuhlangane. Kwakuyikhampani enoqhekeko, futhi uCohren waba nemizwa ehlangene mayela nokukhuphula u-Lieutenant wokuqala esikhundleni, ngokuyinhloko ngenxa yezizathu.
UCohren noNemic, umholi wokuqala wePlatoon, wahamba ndawonye ngaphansi kokukhanya kwezibani eziningi kwamaFOB izibani okuningi, ekhanyiswa igeneretha. Eziningi zinokubomvu ukubasiza bazifihle ezitheni ezibhomayo. IDaybreak iholele ekuhlaseleni kweWild Weasel, kokubili emoyeni nasemhlabeni, ukuba balwe nabo.
“Olunye usuku, omunye umsebenzi weHell’s Frontrunners” kusho uNemic ngohleko olomile. “Basiyisa kuphi?”
“E-FOB ngaphandle kwase-Ianlos. Sithunyelwe ukuba sisize ukuhlasela okusemhlabeni” kuphendula uCohren, edonsa ugwayi wakhe. Abaningi basola uCraith ngokumfundisa ukubhema, kodwa ukuchitha unyaka empini kwenza okuningi kuwe, ngakho akashongo lutho.
“Shit. Kuya kuba kubi phambili,'' kusho uNemic. “Zonke izindaba eziphuma kule ndawo zithi ‘Sekela imizamo yempi. Thumela usizo eKurgan Front' kunganjani kuthunyelwe usizo eHowland Front”
“Ameni mfowethu” kusho uCohren njengoba elahla okusele kogwayi odakeni. “Kunoma yikuphi, siyaphuma neplatoon yokuqala ehlomile, ngakho akudingeki sihambe. UKaputeni uShaw kufanele abe ngowabo”
“UShaw usitholele imoto?” kubuza uNemic, emangele kancane.
“Yebo. Eqinisweni, akukubi njengoba bengicabanga. Ngisho ukuthi akayena umpetha kodwa uyabekezeleleka”
UCohren wakhuphula isithupha nomunwe wokukhomba kuyi-mic yakhe emqaleni, edlulisela ipekhi yakhe ngemva kwakhe ngesikhathi ekwazi. “Wonke amayunithi ku-Exodus Company, ahlangana neMotor Pool West lapho seniqedile. Siyaphuma ne- Armored Platoon yokuqala e-0500”
Yonke imizuzwana uthole izimpendulo ezivela kubaholi bamaqembu. UHaris, uCraith, noRavik bonke bebesezikhundleni ezingaphansi kwese-NCO ngesikhathi befika lapho. Bonke babane bebe ngabangane abahle kusukela babuyela eMhlabeni. Kuzwakala kuyisikhathi eside manje kusukela uCohren aqala ukubabona, ngisho noma kungaphansi kweminyaka emibili. Babengabaholi bamaqembu, Kodwa manje uCraith wayehola i-latoon yesibili yangesonto eledlule, ngemva kokuba umholi owedlule esekhishiwe ekwelashweni ngemva kokudutshulwa i-sniper seDaybreak.
Bevuka eduze kwezimoto zempi, Ameho kaCohren noNemic abheka iqembu lamaKronos Main Battle Tanks ayisishiyagalombili kanye namaStrykers amane. Iqembu labo lama ngomumo, liqinisekisa ukuthi imishini yempi ilungele ukudubula. Ukugqolozela kukaCohren ngokushesha wathola uKaputeni uBoradin Shaw, owayekhuluma nesikhulu sempi seplatoon. Njengob bekhuphuka, uShaw wabheka eceleni wabe esehamba, ngokuvamile ngobuso obubandayo efihla yonke imizwa.
“ULieutenant Nemic…Lieutenant Valturi…” Wathi uCohren ubenza kancane, ebuka isibhamu sikaCohren ngaphambi kokubheka futhi. “Ngikuqinisekisa ngokuthi iqembu selikulungele”
“Yebo mnumzane. Kufanele ngabe lisendleleni manje, silinike isikhathi sokuthatha isilinganiso sabo sokudla”
“Siyaphuma eFOB I-131, amamayela angamashumi amahlanu nanhlanu ngaphandle kwase-Ianlos. Sizosekela impi eqhubekayo nokuhlasela kwamuva kwe-Ianlos ukuze siqede ukuvukela lapho. Ngemva kwalokho sizogibela ezintabeni” kuchaza uShaw. “Hlanganisa amaqembu akho bese nigibela intaba”
Ikhampani yasakazeka, bahlangana ndawonye ngamaqembu futhi ama-sergeants awo abaqwalisa amathenki. UCohren waya ethankini eliphezulu kuyi-convoy, ejoyina uNemic, uCraith, kanye nabaqeqeshwayo abasha. UCohren wabakhumbula befika ezinsukwini ezimbalwa, kodwa wayengazi okuningi ngabo. Ehleli eceleni, elengisa izinyawo eceleni, walungisa iphekhi yakhe kanye nomsakazo, okuxhume endlebeni nakumbhobho wakhe.
“Sawubona Cohren, ingabe uHarris usenalo i-Snowball?” Kubuza uNemic njengoba bezinza.
“Usho inkukhu ayintshontshile?” UCohren wakhumbula ngesikhathi bemntshontsha ekuseni epulazini. “Ya, ngiyaqiniseka”
UCohren wathi jeqe kwlinye lamathenki futhi wabona uHarris neqembu lakhe. Kusukela ngemva kwephekhi yakhe angamane nje enze umnyakazo wenkukhu encane enyakazisa ikhanda layo, ebheka bheka okuzungezile.
“Yebo, usase naye” kuphendula uCohren njengoba umnyango wethanki uvuleka futhi isikhulu sifika ukuzohlola.
“Wonke amathanki ayaphuma” Isikhulu sasho ngokuzola kodwa ngokucacile kuma-headset. Izinjini zamathanki e-platoon nama-Strykers zaduma njengoba ziya phambili. UKronos Cohren wanyakaza njengoba ilungela ukuya phambili, ithatha indawo. Amathenki athatha ukwakheka kwe-wedge njengoba ihamba emathafeni e-Itania. Iziphepho zasebusika zenze ixhaphozi laba yiqhwa namahlathi, kodwa udaka lwangashintsha.
Ngemva kwehora, omunye wabaqeqeshi abasha, uCohren, wakhumbula igama laso lingu-Orson, wakhuluma. “Lieutenant, ubulokhu ula kusukela kuqala impi, angithi?”
“Yebo, i-Operation Firestorm,” kuphendula uCohren. “Sicabanga ukuthi kuzobe sekuphelile emasontweni ambalwa, kodwa…siba thathe kancane”
“Ukuthatha kancane ukubeka ngeziphansi” uNemic wahlanganyela ingxoxo. “Banezikhali eziningi namasosha amaningi kunalokho ebesikulungele. Bakwazile ukudubula phansi i-The UFS Revenant emasontweni amabili okuqala, futhi enyangeni edlule ye-Erebus. Kufanele ukubone emzileni esihamba ngawo lapha”
“Ngakho, ngizomelela iFederation” kusho u-Orson ngokuqiniska. “Angeke ngivumele labo baphekuli ukuba bangisabise”
“Usho lokho manje, kodwa ngokwalokho engikubonile, abaqeqeshwayo abaningi abasha njengawe abaneminyaka eyishumi nesishiyagalombili njengawe bajaha ukungena ngokushesha lapho bezwa izibhamu” kusho uCraith.
“Ngicabanga ukuthi sizothola,” kusho uCohren ngohleko. U-Orson akaqhubekanga nengxoxo.
“Exodus XO, Exodus CO” kusho uCohrens emsakazweni. “Sithola amasignisha okushisa ngamayadi angu-350, amazinga angu-20 angith”
UCohren uzikhuphulile wayaphezu kwethanki wabe esephusha ama-Optic Goggles akhe. Akushintsha ku-Thermal, angakwazi ukubona amasignisha okushisa kude.
“Yebo, ngiyababona” kuphendula uCohren, esebenzisa umbhobho wakhe.
“Isitha?” Kubuza omunye umqeqeshi, uNatayla.
“Angeke ngikwazi ukusho,” kusho uCohren. Wathatha umbhobho wabe esekhuluma. “Exodus Company, ningadubuli ngaphandle kwalapho kukhona odubulayo, asibakhiphe
Njengoba besondela, amasignisha okushisa amancane ashintsha abe amabhaluni athatha isimo esiqinile. Njengoba besondela, omunye wabo wagijima wabe esethatha ngaphambi kokubuyela emuva egqumeni ebebe kulo. Amanani ehla ezindaweni zokudubula.
“Sinabantu” kumemeza uShaw emsakazweni njengoba imikhondo e-olintshi ivela egqumeni. Izinhlamvu zishaye amathanki eceleni njengoba amaShock Troopers aphuma emathankini, bebavikela. I-anti missile yazulazula futhi yashaya phansi ngemuva lesakhiwo, yaqhuma futhi yalahla imfucumfucu kwelinye lamathanki. Elinye lishaye eceleni kweStryker, i-APS-Cerberus, futhi yaqhuma. Iqembu laphuma ngokushesha futhi lafuna indawo yokucasha lapho kuqhuma izinhlamvu.
“I-iron 1-2 ne-1-3, 25 amazinga angithi, amayadi angu-300. Dubulani” Kumemeza isikhulu sethanki le-platoon emsakazweni. I-iron 1-2 ne-1-3 yadubula, amagobolongo abo azulazula ngasegqumeni futhi aqhuma, kwahlakazeka udaka namatshe emoyeni.
“Thumela amaSenti” kumemeza uKnoxx, obebukela igquma ngezipopolo. Ingemuva kuya kokukodwa kweCerberus kwavuleka futhi kwaphuma amasosha angahlomile, efake ama-headset akhethekile. Wamemeza imiyalezo embhobhweni oyisikwele kanye namaSenti amabili, ngaphambili aziwa ngokuthi amaSentinels, aphuma ngokushesha. Izingalo ezizacile zensimbi nemilenze eya phambili njengoba iqhasha. Babehlomile, kodwa izikhali zabo bezigaxwe emhlane.
“Bulale noma uthumbe?” Kwabuza uCraith njengoba bebuka.
“Kubukeka ngathi ukuthumba” kuqagela uCohren njengoba amaSentinels amabili enyamalala emawfini othuli nentuthu. Ukumemeza nokudubula kuvele egqumeni, kodwa ngokushesha kwaphela. Isikhashana ngemva kwalokho amaSentinels amabili abuyela emuva, adonsa abantu ngemuva, amabhuthi abo alandela ngemuva. Lapho befinyelela ukuphepha kwePlatoon balahlela inani phansi, wakhala ngenxa yezinhlungu njengoba bewa phansi odakeni naseqhweni.
UShaw wasondele emuntwini owayeseqala ukusukuma. Ngemva kwalokho waphendukela komunye wamaSentinels. “Bangaki?”
“Bathathu abashonile, mnumzane” kuphendula iSentinel. “Abanye babaleka ngezinyawo”
UShaw wanqekuzisa ikhanda wabe esebheka uCohren noCriath, abebemi eduze. “Nobabili sicela nisivalelele le ndoda?”
